#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:3
msgid "Create opportunities from web contact forms"
msgstr "Ustvari priložnosti iz spletnih kontaktnih obrazcev"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:5
msgid ""
"Adding a contact form to a website makes it easy to convert visitors into "
"leads and opportunities. After a visitor submits their information, an "
"opportunity can be created automatically, and assigned to a designated sales "
"team and salesperson."
msgstr ""
"Dodajanje kontaktnega obrazca na spletno mesto olajša pretvorbo obiskovalcev "
"v potencialne stranke in priložnosti. Ko obiskovalec odda svoje podatke, se "
"lahko priložnost ustvari samodejno in dodeli določeni prodajni ekipi in "
"prodajalcu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:12
msgid "Customize contact forms"
msgstr "Prilagodi kontaktne obrazce"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:14
msgid ""
"By default, the *Contact Us* page on an Odoo website displays a "
"preconfigured contact form. This form can be customized, as needed, to suit "
"the needs of a specific sales team."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto stran *Kontaktirajte nas* na spletnem mestu Odoo prikazuje vnaprej "
"konfigurirani kontaktni obrazec. Ta obrazec je mogoče po potrebi "
"prilagoditi, da ustreza potrebam določene prodajne ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:17
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Website app --> Contact Us`, then "
"click :guilabel:`Edit` in the top-right of the screen to open the web "
"editor. Click on the form building block in the body of the webpage to open "
"the form configuration settings on the right sidebar. The following options "
"are available to customize the contact form from the :guilabel:`From` "
"section of the right sidebar:"
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Spletno mesto --> Kontaktirajte nas`, "
"nato kliknite :guilabel:`Uredi` v zgornjem desnem kotu zaslona, da odprete "
"spletni urejevalnik. Kliknite na gradnik obrazca v telesu spletne strani, da "
"odprete nastavitve konfiguracije obrazca v desni stranski vrstici. Naslednje "
"možnosti so na voljo za prilagoditev kontaktnega obrazca v razdelku "
":guilabel:`From` desne stranske vrstice:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:None
msgid "The form configuration settings on an Odoo website."
msgstr "Nastavitve konfiguracije obrazca na spletnem mestu Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:26
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Action`: the default action for a contact form is :guilabel:`Send "
"an Email`. Select :guilabel:`Create an Opportunity` from the drop-down list "
"to capture the information in the *CRM* app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Action`: privzeto dejanje za kontaktni obrazec je :guilabel:`Send "
"an Email`. Izberite :guilabel:`Create an Opportunity` s spustnega seznama, "
"da zajamete informacije v aplikaciji *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:29
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: choose a sales team from the drop-down menu that the "
"opportunities from this form should be assigned to. This field **only** "
"appears if the :guilabel:`Action` field is set to :guilabel:`Create an "
"Opportunity`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Sales Team`: izberite prodajno ekipo s spustnega menija, kateri "
"naj bodo dodeljene priložnosti iz tega obrazca. To polje se prikaže "
"**samo**, če je polje :guilabel:`Action` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`Create an "
"Opportunity`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:32
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: if the opportunities should be assigned to a "
"specific salesperson, select them from the drop-down menu. If no selection "
"is made in this field, the opportunities are assigned based on the team's "
"existing rules."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salesperson`: če naj bodo priložnosti dodeljene določenemu "
"prodajalcu, ga izberite s spustnega menija. Če v tem polju ni izbire, se "
"priložnosti dodelijo na podlagi obstoječih pravil ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:35
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Marked Fields`: use this field to alter how the form handles "
"marked fields. The default option is to treat marked fields "
"as :guilabel:`Required`, which is the recommended setting."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Marked Fields`: uporabite to polje za spremembo načina, kako "
"obrazec obravnava označena polja. Privzeta možnost je, da se označena polja "
"obravnavajo kot :guilabel:`Required`, kar je priporočena nastavitev."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:37
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Mark Text`: choose how :guilabel:`Marked Fields` should be "
"identified. The default character is an asterisk (`*`)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Mark Text`: izberite, kako naj bodo :guilabel:`Marked Fields` "
"označena. Privzeti znak je zvezdica (`*`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Labels Width`: use this field to alter the pixel width of the "
"labels, if desired."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Labels Width`: uporabite to polje za spremembo širine oznak v "
"pikslih, če je to želeno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On Success`: select how the webpage reacts after a customer "
"successfully submits a form. :guilabel:`Nothing` keeps the customer on the "
"same screen, with the addition of a confirmation message that the form was "
"submitted successfully. :guilabel:`Redirect` sends the customer to a new "
"webpage, based on the address provided in the :guilabel:`URL` field "
"below. :guilabel:`Show Message` replaces the form with a preconfigured "
"message that informs the customer someone should respond to them as soon as "
"possible."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`On Success`: izberite, kako se spletna stran odzove, ko stranka "
"uspešno odda obrazec. :guilabel:`Nothing` obdrži stranko na istem zaslonu z "
"dodatkom potrditvenega sporočila, da je bil obrazec uspešno oddan. "
":guilabel:`Redirect` preusmeri stranko na novo spletno stran na podlagi "
"naslova, podanega v polju :guilabel:`URL` spodaj. :guilabel:`Show Message` "
"nadomesti obrazec z vnaprej konfiguriranim sporočilom, ki stranko obvešča, "
"da ji bo nekdo odgovoril čim prej."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:46
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL`: if :guilabel:`Redirect` is selected in the :guilabel:`On "
"Success` field, enter the URL for the webpage, where customers should be "
"directed after successfully submitting a form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL`: če je v polju :guilabel:`On Success` izbrano "
":guilabel:`Redirect`, vnesite URL spletne strani, kamor naj bodo stranke "
"usmerjene po uspešni oddaji obrazca."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:48
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visibility`: use the drop-down menu to add any visibility "
"conditions for this field, if desired."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vidnost`: uporabite spustni meni, če želite dodati kakršne koli "
"pogoje vidnosti za to polje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:52
msgid ""
"If *leads* are activated in *CRM* settings, selecting :guilabel:`Create an "
"Opportunity` generates a lead instead. To activate leads, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če so v nastavitvah *CRM* aktivirani *potencialni posli*, izbira "
":guilabel:`Ustvari priložnost` namesto tega ustvari potencialni posel. Za "
"aktiviranje potencialnih poslov se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"CRM --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in označite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Potencialni posli`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:57
msgid "Customize contact form fields"
msgstr "Prilagoditev polj kontaktnega obrazca"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:59
msgid ""
"In addition to the settings for the form, the settings for each field can be "
"customized, as well. With the web editor menu still open, click into a field "
"to open the :guilabel:`Field` configuration settings section on the sidebar. "
"The following options are available to customize a field:"
msgstr ""
"Poleg nastavitev za obrazec je mogoče prilagoditi tudi nastavitve za vsako "
"polje. Ko je meni spletnega urejevalnika še vedno odprt, kliknite na polje, "
"da odprete razdelek nastavitev konfiguracije :guilabel:`Polje` v stranski "
"vrstici. Na voljo so naslednje možnosti za prilagoditev polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: choose a custom field option or an existing field type."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta`: izberite možnost prilagojenega polja ali obstoječo vrsto "
"polja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Input Type`: determine the type of information customers should "
"input. Available options "
"are :guilabel:`Text`, :guilabel:`Email`, :guilabel:`Telephone`, "
"or :guilabel:`Url`. The selection made in this field limits the format that "
"customers can use when entering information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta vnosa`: določite vrsto informacij, ki jih morajo vnesti "
"stranke. Na voljo so možnosti :guilabel:`Besedilo`, :guilabel:`E-pošta`, "
":guilabel:`Telefon` ali :guilabel:`URL`. Izbira v tem polju omejuje obliko "
"zapisa, ki jo lahko stranke uporabijo pri vnosu informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:67
msgid ":guilabel:`Label`: enter the name for the field."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Oznaka`: vnesite ime polja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Position`: choose the way the label is aligned with the rest of "
"the form. The label can be hidden, above the field, to the left of the "
"field, or right adjusted and closer to the field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Položaj`: izberite način poravnave oznake z ostalo vsebino "
"obrazca. Oznaka je lahko skrita, nad poljem, levo od polja ali poravnana "
"desno in bližje polju."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:70
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Description`: slide the toggle to add a description for the "
"field, which can provide additional instructions to customers. Click under "
"the field on the form to add the description."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Opis`: premaknite stikalo, če želite dodati opis polja, ki lahko "
"strankam zagotovi dodatna navodila. Kliknite pod polje na obrazcu, če želite "
"dodati opis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Placeholder`: enter an example to help users know how to input "
"information where formatting is important, such as a phone number or email "
"address."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Namestnik`: vnesite primer, ki uporabnikom pomaga razumeti, kako "
"vnesti informacije, kjer je oblikovanje pomembno, na primer telefonska "
"številka ali e-poštni naslov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:74
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Default Value`: enter a value to include in the form, by default, "
"if the customer does not provide information in the field. *It is not "
"recommended to include a default value for required fields*."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Privzeta vrednost`: vnesite vrednost, ki naj bo privzeto "
"vključena v obrazec, če stranka ne navede informacij v polju. *Ne priporoča "
"se vključitev privzete vrednosti za obvezna polja*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:77
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Required`: slide the toggle to mark this field as required if it "
"**must** be filled in for every submission."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Obvezno`: premaknite stikalo, če želite to polje označiti kot "
"obvezno, če **mora** biti izpolnjeno pri vsaki oddaji."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:79
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Visibility`: select when this field should be visible. Use the "
"button on the left to choose whether to show or hide this field on a desktop "
"users. Use the button on the right to choose whether to show or hide this "
"field to mobile users."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vidnost`: izberite, kdaj naj bo to polje vidno. Uporabite gumb na "
"levi, če želite izbrati, ali naj bo to polje prikazano ali skrito "
"uporabnikom namiznih naprav. Uporabite gumb na desni, če želite izbrati, ali "
"naj bo to polje prikazano ali skrito mobilnim uporabnikom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:82
msgid ":guilabel:`Animation`: select if this field should have any animation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Animacija`: izberite, ali naj ima to polje kakršno koli animacijo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:None
msgid "The field configuration settings on an Odoo website."
msgstr "Nastavitve konfiguracije polja na spletnem mestu Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:89
msgid "View opportunities"
msgstr "Ogled priložnosti"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:91
msgid ""
"After a customer submits a contact form, and an opportunity is created, it "
"is assigned based on the :ref:`form settings <crm/customize-contact-form>`. "
"To view opportunities, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My "
"Pipeline`."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranka odda kontaktni obrazec in je ustvarjena priložnost, se dodeli na "
"podlagi :ref:`nastavitev obrazca <crm/customize-contact-form>`. Za ogled "
"priložnosti se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija CRM --> Prodaja --> "
"Moj cevovod`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:96
msgid ""
"If leads are activated on the database, contact form submissions are "
"generated as leads, not opportunities. To activate leads, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and tick "
"the :guilabel:`Leads` checkbox. Then, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če so potencialni posli aktivirani v zbirki podatkov, se oddaje kontaktnega "
"obrazca ustvarijo kot potencialni posli, ne priložnosti. Za aktiviranje "
"potencialnih poslov se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija CRM --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in označite potrditveno polje "
":guilabel:`Potencialni posli`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:100
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Leads` to view the newly-created "
"leads."
msgstr ""
"Pomaknite se na :menuselection:`Aplikacija CRM --> Potencialni posli`, če "
"želite videti novo ustvarjene potencialne posle."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:102
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`My Pipeline` dashboard, click on an opportunity card in "
"the Kanban view to open the opportunity record. The information submitted by "
"the customer is visible on the opportunity record."
msgstr ""
"Na nadzorni plošči :guilabel:`Moj cevovod` kliknite na kartico priložnosti v "
"pogledu Kanban, da odprete zapis priložnosti. Informacije, ki jih je oddala "
"stranka, so vidne v zapisu priložnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:107
msgid ""
"As the contact form fields are customizable, the fields on the opportunity "
"record, where the form information is stored, varies accordingly."
msgstr ""
"Ker so polja obrazca za stike prilagodljiva, se polja na zapisu priložnosti, "
"kjer so shranjene informacije iz obrazca, ustrezno razlikujejo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:110
msgid ""
"If the preconfigured contact form is used, the *Subject* field is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Title` field, and the content in the :guilabel:`Notes` field, "
"which is labeled as :guilabel:`Your Question`, is added to "
"the :guilabel:`Internal Notes` tab."
msgstr ""
"Če se uporabi vnaprej nastavljen obrazec za stike, se polje *Zadeva* doda k "
"polju :guilabel:`Naslov`, vsebina v polju :guilabel:`Opombe`, ki je označeno "
"kot :guilabel:`Vaše vprašanje`, pa se doda na zavihek :guilabel:`Notranje "
"opombe`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:115
msgid ":doc:`../pipeline/manage_sales_teams`"
msgstr ":doc:`../pipeline/manage_sales_teams`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:116
msgid ":doc:`convert`"
msgstr ":doc:`convert`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:117
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/manage_sales_teams.rst:109
msgid ":doc:`../track_leads/lead_scoring`"
msgstr ":doc:`../track_leads/lead_scoring`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/opportunities_form.rst:118
msgid ":ref:`Website forms <website/building_blocks/form>`"
msgstr ":ref:`Spletni obrazci <website/building_blocks/form>`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:3
msgid "Create and send quotations"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in pošiljanje ponudb"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:5
msgid ""
"Once a qualified lead has been converted into an opportunity, the next step "
"is to create and deliver a quotation. This process can be easily handled "
"through Odoo's *CRM* application."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kvalificirana pobuda pretvorjena v priložnost, je naslednji korak "
"ustvarjanje in dostava ponudbe. Ta postopek je mogoče enostavno upravljati "
"prek Odoo aplikacije *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:9
msgid "Create a new quotation"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje nove ponudbe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:11
msgid ""
"To create a new quotation, open the :menuselection:`CRM app`, revealing "
"the :guilabel:`Pipeline` page on the main *CRM* dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove ponudbe odprite :menuselection:`aplikacijo CRM`, kar "
"prikaže stran :guilabel:`Cevovod` na glavni nadzorni plošči aplikacije *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:14
msgid ""
"From here, click on any opportunity to open it. Review the existing "
"information and update any fields, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Od tu kliknite na katero koli priložnost, da jo odprete. Preglejte obstoječe "
"informacije in po potrebi posodobite polja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:18
msgid ""
"If a quotation has already been created for this opportunity, it can be "
"found by clicking on the :guilabel:`Quotations` smart button at the top of "
"the top of the form. The number of existing quotations is listed on the "
"smart button, as well."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila ponudba za to priložnost že ustvarjena, jo najdete s klikom na "
"pametni gumb :guilabel:`Ponudbe` na vrhu obrazca. Število obstoječih ponudb "
"je navedeno tudi na pametnem gumbu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:22
msgid ""
"At the top-left of the form, click the :guilabel:`New Quotation` button."
msgstr "V zgornjem levem delu obrazca kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Nova ponudba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:None
msgid "Qualified lead form with New Quotation button emphasized."
msgstr "Obrazec kvalificirane pobude z označenim gumbom Nova ponudba."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:29
msgid ""
"The **Sales** application **must** be installed for the :guilabel:`New "
"Quotation` button to appear."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz gumba :guilabel:`Nova ponudba` **mora** biti nameščena aplikacija "
"**Sales**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:33
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Customer` field is **not** required on the opportunity form."
msgstr "Polje :guilabel:`Stranka` **ni** zahtevano na obrazcu priložnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:35
msgid ""
"However, customer information must be added or linked before a quotation can "
"be sent. If the :guilabel:`Customer` field is left blank on the opportunity, "
"clicking the :guilabel:`New Quotation` button opens a pop-up window with the "
"following options:"
msgstr ""
"Vendar je treba podatke o stranki dodati ali povezati, preden je mogoče "
"ponudbo poslati. Če polje :guilabel:`Stranka` na priložnosti ostane prazno, "
"klik na gumb :guilabel:`Nova ponudba` odpre pojavno okno z naslednjimi "
"možnostmi:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:39
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Create a new customer`: creates a new customer record, using any "
"available information provided on the opportunity form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ustvarjanje nove stranke`: ustvari nov zapis stranke z uporabo "
"vseh razpoložljivih informacij, podanih na obrazcu priložnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Link to an existing customer`: opens a drop-down field with "
"existing customer names. Select a name to link this new quotation to an "
"existing customer record."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Povezovanje z obstoječo stranko`: odpre spustno polje z imeni "
"obstoječih strank. Izberite ime za povezavo te nove ponudbe z obstoječim "
"zapisom stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Do not link to a customer`: the quotation will **not** be linked "
"to a customer, and no changes are made to the customer information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ne poveži s stranko`: ponudba **ne** bo povezana s stranko in na "
"podatkih o stranki ni sprememb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:46
msgid ""
"Once this button is clicked, a new quotation form appears. Confirm the "
"information in the top half of the form, and update any missing or incorrect "
"fields:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta gumb kliknjen, se pojavi nov obrazec za ponudbo. Potrdite "
"informacije v zgornji polovici obrazca in posodobite morebitna manjkajoča "
"ali nepravilna polja:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:49
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Customer`: the company or contact for whom this quotation was "
"created."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stranka`: podjetje ali kontakt, za katerega je bila ta ponudba "
"ustvarjena."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:50
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Referrer`: if this customer was referred by another customer or "
"contact, select it from the drop-down menu in this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Priporočitelj`: če je to stranko priporočila druga stranka ali "
"kontakt, jo izberite iz spustnega menija v tem polju."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:52
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Address`: physical address where the invoice should be "
"sent."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naslov za račun`: fizični naslov, na katerega je treba poslati "
"račun."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:53
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Address`: physical address where any products should be "
"delivered."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naslov za dostavo`: fizični naslov, na katerega je treba "
"dostaviti izdelke."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotation Template`: if applicable, select a pre-"
"configured :doc:`quotation template <../../sales/sales_quotations/"
"quote_template>` from this field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Predloga ponudbe`: če je primerno, izberite vnaprej konfigurirano "
":doc:`predlogo ponudbe <../../sales/sales_quotations/quote_template>` iz "
"tega polja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:56
msgid ":guilabel:`Expiration`: date when this quotation is no longer valid."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Potek`: datum, ko ta ponudba ni več veljavna."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:57
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Quotation Date`: creation date of draft/sent orders, confirmation "
"date of confirmed orders. Note that this field is only visible "
"if :doc:`Developer mode (debug mode) </applications/general/developer_mode>` "
"is active."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Datum ponudbe`: datum nastanka osnutkov/poslanih naročil, datum "
"potrditve potrjenih naročil. Upoštevajte, da je to polje vidno le, če je "
"aktiven :doc:`razvijalski način (način za odpravljanje napak) </applications/"
"general/developer_mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:60
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Recurring Plan`: if this quotation is for a recurring product or "
"subscription, select the recurring plan configuration to be used."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ponavljajoči načrt`: če je ta ponudba za ponavljajoči izdelek ali "
"naročnino, izberite konfiguracijo ponavljajočega načrta, ki naj se uporabi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:62
msgid ":guilabel:`Pricelist`: select a pricelist to be applied to this order."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Cenik`: izberite cenik, ki naj se uporabi za to naročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Payment Terms`: select any applicable payment terms for this "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Plačilni pogoji`: izberite vse veljavne plačilne pogoje za to "
"ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Expiration` field automatically populates based on the "
"creation date of the quotation, and the default validity time frame."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Potek` se samodejno izpolni na podlagi datuma nastanka "
"ponudbe in privzetega časovnega okvira veljavnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:73
msgid ""
"To update the default validity time frame, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Configuration --> Settings --> Quotations & Orders` and update "
"the :guilabel:`Default Quotation Validity` field. To disable automatic "
"expiration, enter `0` in this field."
msgstr ""
"Za posodobitev privzetega časovnega okvira veljavnosti pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve --> "
"Ponudbe in naročila` in posodobite polje :guilabel:`Privzeta veljavnost "
"ponudbe`. Za onemogočanje samodejnega poteka vnesite `0` v to polje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:77
msgid "When the desired changes are complete, click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr "Ko so želene spremembe končane, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:79
msgid ""
"When using a quotation template, the expiration date is based off of "
"the :guilabel:`Quotation Validity` field on the template. To alter the "
"validity date computation on a template, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Sales Orders --> Quotation Templates`."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi predloge ponudbe temelji datum poteka na polju "
":guilabel:`Veljavnost ponudbe` v predlogi. Za spremembo izračuna datuma "
"veljavnosti v predlogi pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Prodajna naročila --> Predloge ponudb`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:83
msgid ""
"Then, click on a template to open it, and update the number in "
"the :guilabel:`Quotation Validity` field."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite na predlogo, da jo odprete, in posodobite število v polju "
":guilabel:`Veljavnost ponudbe`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:87
msgid "Order lines"
msgstr "Postavke naročila"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:89
msgid ""
"After updating the customer, payment, and deadline information on the new "
"quotation, the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab can be updated with the "
"appropriate product information."
msgstr ""
"Po posodobitvi informacij o stranki, plačilu in roku na novi ponudbi lahko "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila` posodobite z ustreznimi informacijami o "
"izdelku."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:92
msgid ""
"To do that, click :guilabel:`Add a product` in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"To storite tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj izdelek` v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Vrstice naročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:94
msgid ""
"Next, type the name of an item into the :guilabel:`Product` field to search "
"through the product catalog. Then, select a product from the drop-down menu, "
"or create a new one by selecting :guilabel:`Create` or :guilabel:`Create and "
"Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Nato v polje :guilabel:`Izdelek` vnesite ime artikla za iskanje po katalogu "
"izdelkov. Nato izberite izdelek iz spustnega menija ali ustvarite novega z "
"izbiro :guilabel:`Ustvari` ali :guilabel:`Ustvari in uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:98
msgid ""
"After selecting a product, update the :guilabel:`Quantity`, if necessary. "
"Confirm the information in the remaining fields."
msgstr ""
"Po izbiri izdelka po potrebi posodobite :guilabel:`Količino`. Potrdite "
"informacije v preostalih poljih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:101
msgid ""
"To remove a line from the quotation, click the :icon:`fa-trash-"
"o` :guilabel:`(trash can)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti vrstico iz ponudbe, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-trash-o` "
":guilabel:`(koš za smeti)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:103
msgid ""
"To organize products into sections click :guilabel:`Add a section` and type "
"a name for the section. Then, click the :icon:`oi-"
"draggable` :guilabel:`(drag)` icon to the left of the name and drag to move "
"the section to the appropriate location. Move each product using the same "
"method to finish organizing the quotation order lines."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izdelke organizirati v razdelke, kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"razdelek` in vnesite ime razdelka. Nato kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-draggable` "
":guilabel:`(povleci)` levo od imena in povlecite, da premaknete razdelek na "
"ustrezno mesto. Premaknite vsak izdelek z isto metodo, da dokončate "
"organizacijo vrstic naročila ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:None
msgid ""
"Categories are used to create separate sections on the order lines of a "
"quote."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije se uporabljajo za ustvarjanje ločenih razdelkov v vrsticah "
"naročila ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:113
msgid "Product catalog"
msgstr "Katalog izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:115
msgid ""
"To quickly add numerous products to the quotation, click "
"the :guilabel:`Catalog` button to open the product catalog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite hitro dodati številne izdelke v ponudbo, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Katalog`, da odprete katalog izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:118
msgid ""
"All products in the database are listed as cards and can be sorted in the "
"left panel by :guilabel:`Product Category` and :guilabel:`Attributes`."
msgstr ""
"Vsi izdelki v bazi podatkov so navedeni kot kartice in jih je mogoče "
"razvrstiti v levem pultu po :guilabel:`Kategoriji izdelka` in "
":guilabel:`Atributih`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:None
msgid "The product catalog displays all products as cards."
msgstr "Katalog izdelkov prikazuje vse izdelke kot kartice."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:125
msgid ""
"To add a product, click the :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` :guilabel:`Add` button "
"on the product card. Set the quantity of the item using the :icon:`fa-"
"plus` :guilabel:`(add)` or :icon:`fa-minus` :guilabel:`(subtract)` buttons, "
"or type the quantity in the number field between the two buttons. To remove "
"an item, click the :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Remove` button on the product "
"card."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati izdelek, kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` "
":guilabel:`Dodaj` na kartici izdelka. Nastavite količino artikla z uporabo "
"gumbov :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(dodaj)` ali :icon:`fa-minus` :guilabel:`"
"(odštej)` ali vnesite količino v številčno polje med gumboma. Če želite "
"odstraniti artikel, kliknite gumb :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`Odstrani` na "
"kartici izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The purple add and subtract buttons are used to set the quantity of an item."
msgstr ""
"Vijolična gumba za dodajanje in odštevanje se uporabljata za nastavitev "
"količine artikla."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:134
msgid ""
"Once all product quantities are set, click the :guilabel:`Back to Quotation` "
"button to return to the quotation. The items selected in the product catalog "
"now appear in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vse količine izdelkov nastavljene, kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Nazaj na "
"ponudbo`, da se vrnete na ponudbo. Artikli, izbrani v katalogu izdelkov, se "
"zdaj pojavijo v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:138
msgid "Preview and send quotation"
msgstr "Predogled in pošiljanje ponudbe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:140
msgid ""
"To see a preview of the quotation as the customer will see it, click "
"the :guilabel:`Preview` button. Doing so opens a preview in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Portal`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti predogled ponudbe, kot jo bo videl stranka, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Predogled`. S tem se odpre predogled v :guilabel:`Portalu za "
"stranke`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:143
msgid ""
"After reviewing the customer preview, click :guilabel:`Return to edit mode` "
"to return to the quotation form in the backend."
msgstr ""
"Po pregledu predogleda za stranko kliknite :guilabel:`Vrnitev v način "
"urejanja`, da se vrnete na obrazec ponudbe v zalednem sistemu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:146
msgid ""
"When the quotation is ready to deliver to the customer, click "
"the :guilabel:`Send by Email` button."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ponudba pripravljena za dostavo stranki, kliknite gumb "
":guilabel:`Pošlji po e-pošti`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:148
msgid ""
"Doing so opens a pop-up window with a pre-configured email message. "
"Information from the quotation, including the contact information, total "
"cost, and quotation title are be imported from the quotation."
msgstr ""
"S tem se odpre pojavno okno s vnaprej konfigurirano e-poštno sporočilo. "
"Informacije iz ponudbe, vključno s kontaktnimi podatki, skupnimi stroški in "
"naslovom ponudbe, so uvožene iz ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:152
msgid "A PDF of the quotation is added as an attachment to the email."
msgstr "PDF ponudbe je dodan kot priloga e-poštnemu sporočilu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:155
msgid ""
"A pre-loaded template is used to create the email message. To alter the "
"template, click the internal link to the right of the :guilabel:`Load "
"template` field, located at the bottom of the email pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Vnaprej naložena predloga se uporablja za ustvarjanje e-poštnega sporočila. "
"Če želite spremeniti predlogo, kliknite notranjo povezavo desno od polja "
":guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`, ki se nahaja na dnu pojavnega okna e-pošte."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:159
msgid ""
"To select a new template, select an option from the :guilabel:`Load "
"template` drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrati novo predlogo, izberite možnost iz spustnega menija "
":guilabel:`Naloži predlogo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:161
msgid ""
"Proceed to make any necessary changes to the email, then "
"click :guilabel:`Send`. A copy of the message is added to the *Chatter* of "
"the of the record."
msgstr ""
"Izvedite potrebne spremembe e-pošte in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji`. "
"Kopija sporočila je dodana v *Klepetalniku* zapisa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:164
msgid ""
"After a quotation is sent, the originating "
"opportunity's :guilabel:`Quotations` smart button updates with a new count. "
"This quotation, and all other quotations can be accessed through this smart "
"button at the top of the opportunity in the *CRM* app."
msgstr ""
"Po pošiljanju ponudbe se pametni gumb :guilabel:`Ponudbe` izvorne "
"priložnosti posodobi z novim štetjem. Ta ponudba in vse druge ponudbe so "
"dostopne prek tega pametnega gumba na vrhu priložnosti v aplikaciji *CRM*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:168
msgid ""
"Any quotations attached to the opportunity that are confirmed, and have "
"therefore been converted to sales orders, will be deducted from the number "
"listed on the :guilabel:`Quotations` smart button. Instead, the value of the "
"sales order will appear in the :guilabel:`Orders` smart button located in "
"the same control panel."
msgstr ""
"Vse ponudbe, priložene priložnosti, ki so potrjene in so bile zato "
"pretvorjene v prodajne naloge, bodo odštete od števila, navedenega na "
"pametnem gumbu :guilabel:`Ponudbe`. Namesto tega se bo vrednost prodajnega "
"naloga prikazala na pametnem gumbu :guilabel:`Naročila`, ki se nahaja na "
"istem nadzornem pultu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:174
msgid "Mark an opportunity won or lost"
msgstr "Označi priložnost kot pridobljeno ali izgubljeno"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:176
msgid ""
"In order to keep the pipeline up to date and accurate, opportunities need to "
"be identified as *won* or *lost* once a customer has responded to a "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bil cevovod posodobljen in točen, je treba priložnosti označiti kot "
"*pridobljene* ali *izgubljene*, ko se stranke odzovejo na ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:179
msgid ""
"To mark an opportunity as *won* or *lost*, return to the opportunity using "
"the breadcrumbs at the top-left of the quotation form. Or navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Sales --> My Pipeline` and click on the "
"correct opportunity to open it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite priložnost označiti kot *pridobljeno* ali *izgubljeno*, se vrnite "
"na priložnost z uporabo drobtinic v zgornjem levem kotu obrazca ponudbe. Ali "
"se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija CRM --> Prodaja --> Moj cevovod` "
"in kliknite na pravilno priložnost, da jo odprete."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:183
msgid ""
"At the top-left of the form, click on either the :guilabel:`Won` "
"or :guilabel:`Lost` button."
msgstr ""
"V zgornjem levem kotu obrazca kliknite na gumb :guilabel:`Pridobljeno` ali "
":guilabel:`Izgubljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:185
msgid ""
"If the opportunity is marked *won*, a green :guilabel:`Won` banner is added "
"to the record, and it is moved to the :guilabel:`Won` stage."
msgstr ""
"Če je priložnost označena kot *pridobljena*, se zapisu doda zelen pasek "
":guilabel:`Pridobljeno` in premakne se v fazo :guilabel:`Pridobljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:188
msgid ""
"Marking an opportunity as *lost*, via the :guilabel:`Lost` button opens "
"a :guilabel:`Mark Lost` pop-up window, where a :guilabel:`Lost Reason` can "
"be entered."
msgstr ""
"Označevanje priložnosti kot *izgubljene* prek gumba :guilabel:`Izgubljeno` "
"odpre pojavno okno :guilabel:`Označi kot izgubljeno`, kjer je mogoče vnesti "
":guilabel:`Razlog izgube`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:191
msgid ""
"From the :guilabel:`Lost Reason` drop-down field, choose an existing lost "
"reason. If no applicable reason is available, create a new one by entering "
"it into the :guilabel:`Lost Reason` field, and clicking :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr ""
"V spustnem polju :guilabel:`Razlog izgube` izberite obstoječi razlog izgube. "
"Če ustrezen razlog ni na voljo, ustvarite novega tako, da ga vnesete v polje "
":guilabel:`Razlog izgube` in kliknete :guilabel:`Ustvari`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:196
msgid ""
"It's best practice to try and use pre-configured :guilabel:`Lost Reason` "
"values as much as possible or to limit the creation of new values only to "
"sales team leads. Using consistent values for this parameter will make "
"pipeline analysis easier and more accurate when filtering for "
"the :guilabel:`Lost Reason` parameter."
msgstr ""
"Najboljša praksa je poskusiti čim bolj uporabiti vnaprej nastavljene "
"vrednosti :guilabel:`Razlog izgube` ali omejiti ustvarjanje novih vrednosti "
"le na vodje prodajnih ekip. Uporaba doslednih vrednosti za ta parameter bo "
"olajšala in naredila bolj natančno analizo cevovoda pri filtriranju po "
"parametru :guilabel:`Razlog izgube`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:201
msgid ""
"To set up new values for this field, navigate to :menuselection:`CRM --> "
"Configuration --> Lost Reasons`, and click both :guilabel:`New` "
"and :guilabel:`Save` for each new entry added to the list."
msgstr ""
"Če želite nastaviti nove vrednosti za to polje, se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`CRM --> Konfiguracija --> Razlogi izgube` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo` in :guilabel:`Shrani` za vsak nov vnos, dodan na seznam."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:205
msgid ""
"Additional notes and comments can be added in the :guilabel:`Closing Note` "
"field."
msgstr ""
"Dodatna opomba in komentarje je mogoče dodati v polje :guilabel:`Zaključna "
"opomba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:207
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/lost_opportunities.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/pipeline/lost_opportunities.rst:179
msgid ""
"When all the desired information has been entered in the :guilabel:`Mark "
"Lost` pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Mark as Lost`."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi želeni podatki vneseni v pojavno okno :guilabel:`Označi kot "
"izgubljeno`, kliknite :guilabel:`Označi kot izgubljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:210
msgid ""
"Upon clicking :guilabel:`Mark as Lost`, the pop-up window disappears, and "
"Odoo returns to the opportunity form, where a new red :guilabel:`Lost` "
"banner is now present in the upper-right corner of the opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Označi kot izgubljeno` pojavno okno izgine in Odoo se "
"vrne na obrazec priložnosti, kjer je zdaj v zgornjem desnem kotu priložnosti "
"prisoten nov rdeč pasek :guilabel:`Izgubljeno`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:214
msgid ""
"Once an opportunity is marked as *lost*, it is no longer considered active, "
"and it is removed from the pipeline."
msgstr ""
"Ko je priložnost označena kot *izgubljena*, se ne šteje več kot aktivna in "
"je odstranjena iz cevovoda."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:217
msgid ""
"In order to view a *lost* opportunity from the pipeline, click "
"the :guilabel:`down arrow icon` to the right of the search bar, and select "
"either :guilabel:`Lost` or :guilabel:`Archived` from the drop-down menu that "
"appears."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati *izgubljeno* priložnost iz cevovoda, kliknite na "
":guilabel:`ikono puščice navzdol` na desni strani iskalne vrstice in v "
"spustnem meniju, ki se prikaže, izberite :guilabel:`Izgubljeno` ali "
":guilabel:`Arhivirano`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/send_quotes.rst:222
msgid ""
"While opportunities that have been marked as *lost* are considered "
"*Archived*, be advised that, in order for an opportunity to be included as "
"*lost* in reporting, it **must** be specifically marked as *lost*, not "
"*Archived*."
msgstr ""
"Čeprav se priložnosti, ki so bile označene kot *izgubljene*, štejejo za "
"*arhivirane*, upoštevajte, da mora biti priložnost, da bo vključena kot "
"*izgubljena* v poročila, **izrecno** označena kot *izgubljena*, ne "
"*arhivirana*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize.rst:5
msgid "Optimize your Day-to-Day work"
msgstr "Optimizirajte svoje vsakodnevno delo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:3
msgid "CRM Gamification"
msgstr "CRM igrifikacija"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:5
msgid ""
"In Odoo's *CRM* app, *gamification tools* provide the opportunity to "
"evaluate and motivate users through customizable challenges, goals, and "
"rewards. Goals are created to target actions within the *CRM* app, and can "
"be tracked and rewarded automatically to participating sales teams."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji *CRM* Odoo *orodja za igričenje* omogočajo ocenjevanje in "
"motiviranje uporabnikov prek prilagodljivih izzivov, ciljev in nagrad. Cilji "
"so ustvarjeni za ciljanje dejanj v aplikaciji *CRM* in jih je mogoče "
"samodejno spremljati in nagraditi sodelujoče prodajne ekipe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:12
msgid ""
"To install the *CRM Gamification* module, navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Apps` application. Click into the :guilabel:`Search...` "
"bar at the top of the page and remove the :guilabel:`Apps` filter. Type `CRM "
"Gamification` to search."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev modula *CRM Gamification* se pomaknite na aplikacijo "
":menuselection:`Aplikacije`. Kliknite v vrstico :guilabel:`Iskanje...` na "
"vrhu strani in odstranite filter :guilabel:`Aplikacije`. Za iskanje vnesite "
"`CRM Gamification`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:16
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`CRM Gamification` module, click :guilabel:`Install`. This "
"module features goals and challenges related to the *CRM* and *Sales* "
"applications."
msgstr ""
"Na modulu :guilabel:`CRM Gamification` kliknite :guilabel:`Namesti`. Ta "
"modul vsebuje cilje in izzive, povezane z aplikacijama *CRM* in *Prodaja*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:None
msgid "View of the gamification module being installed in Odoo."
msgstr "Pogled nameščenega modula igrifikacije v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:24
msgid ""
"If **both** the *CRM* and *Sales* apps are installed, the *CRM Gamification* "
"module is automatically installed on the database."
msgstr ""
"Če sta **obe** aplikaciji *CRM* in *Prodaja* nameščeni, se modul *CRM "
"Gamification* samodejno namesti v bazo podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:27
msgid ""
"To access the *Gamification Tools* menu, first enable :ref:`developer-mode`."
msgstr ""
"Za dostop do menija *Orodja za igrifikacijo* najprej omogočite "
":ref:`developer-mode`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:29
msgid "Next, navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> Gamification Tools`."
msgstr ""
"Nato se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Nastavitve --> Orodja za "
"igrifikacijo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:None
msgid "View if the gamification tools menu in Odoo Settings."
msgstr "Pogled menija orodij za igrifikacijo v nastavitvah Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:38
msgid "Create badges"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje značk"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:40
msgid ""
"*Badges* are awarded to users when they have completed a challenge. "
"Different badges can be awarded based on the type of task completed, and can "
"be issued to more than one user, depending on the time they accomplish the "
"goal."
msgstr ""
"*Značke* se dodelijo uporabnikom, ko dokončajo izziv. Različne značke se "
"lahko dodelijo glede na vrsto dokončanega opravila in jih lahko prejme več "
"kot en uporabnik, odvisno od časa, ko dosežejo cilj."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:44
msgid ""
"To view the existing badges, or create a new one, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Gamification Tools --> Badges`."
msgstr ""
"Za ogled obstoječih značk ali ustvarjanje nove se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`Nastavitve --> Orodja za igrifikacijo --> Značke`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:None
msgid "View of the badges page in Odoo."
msgstr "Pogled strani značk v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:52
msgid ""
"Some badges can be awarded outside of challenges, as well. Select the Kanban "
"card for the desired badge, then click :guilabel:`Grant`. This opens "
"a :guilabel:`Grant Badge` pop-up window. Select a user from "
"the :guilabel:`Who would you like to reward?` field."
msgstr ""
"Nekatere značke se lahko dodelijo tudi zunaj izzivov. Izberite kartico "
"Kanban za želeno značko, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodeli`. To odpre pojavno "
"okno :guilabel:`Dodeli značko`. Izberite uporabnika iz polja :guilabel:`Koga "
"želite nagraditi?`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:56
msgid ""
"Add any additional information regarding why the user is receiving the "
"reward in the field below, then click :guilabel:`Grant Badge`."
msgstr ""
"V spodnje polje dodajte morebitne dodatne informacije o tem, zakaj uporabnik "
"prejema nagrado, nato kliknite :guilabel:`Dodeli značko`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:59
msgid ""
"To create a new badge, click :guilabel:`New` at the top-left of the page to "
"open a blank form. Enter a name for the :guilabel:`Badge`, followed by a "
"description."
msgstr ""
"Za ustvarjanje nove značke kliknite :guilabel:`Novo` v zgornjem levem delu "
"strani, da odprete prazen obrazec. Vnesite ime za :guilabel:`Značko`, nato "
"dodajte opis."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:62
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Allowance to Grant` field determines when a badge can be "
"granted, and by whom:"
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Dovoljenje za dodeljevanje` določa, kdaj in kdo lahko "
"dodeli značko:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:64
msgid ":guilabel:`Everyone`: this badge can be manually granted by any user."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vsi`: to značko lahko ročno dodeli katerikoli uporabnik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:65
msgid ""
":guilabel:`A selected list of users`: this badge can only be granted by a "
"select group of users. If this option is selected, it generates a new "
"field, :guilabel:`Authorized Users`. Choose the appropriate users from this "
"drop-down list."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Izbrani seznam uporabnikov`: to značko lahko dodeli samo izbrana "
"skupina uporabnikov. Če je ta možnost izbrana, se ustvari novo polje "
":guilabel:`Pooblaščeni uporabniki`. Iz tega spustnega seznama izberite "
"ustrezne uporabnike."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:68
msgid ""
":guilabel:`People having some badges`: this badge can only be granted by "
"users who have already been awarded a specific badge. If this option is "
"selected it generates a new field, :guilabel:`Required Badges`. Use this "
"drop-down list to select the badge(s) a user must have before they can award "
"this badge to others."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ljudje z določenimi značkami`: to značko lahko dodelijo samo "
"uporabniki, ki so že prejeli določeno značko. Če je ta možnost izbrana, se "
"ustvari novo polje :guilabel:`Zahtevane značke`. Uporabite ta spustni seznam "
"za izbiro značke/značk, ki jih mora imeti uporabnik, preden lahko dodeli to "
"značko drugim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`No one, assigned through challenges`: this badge cannot be "
"manually granted, it can only be awarded through challenges."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Nihče, dodeljuje se prek izzivov`: te značke ni mogoče ročno "
"dodeliti, dodeljuje se lahko samo prek izzivov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:75
msgid ""
"To limit the number of badges a user can send, tick the :guilabel:`Monthly "
"Limited Spending` checkbox. This sets a limit on the number of times a user "
"can grant this badge. In the :guilabel:`Limitation Number` field, enter the "
"maximum number of times this badge can be sent per month, per person."
msgstr ""
"Za omejitev števila značk, ki jih lahko uporabnik pošlje, označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Mesečna omejena poraba`. To nastavi omejitev "
"števila, kolikokrat lahko uporabnik dodeli to značko. V polje "
":guilabel:`Število omejitev` vnesite največje število, kolikokrat lahko ta "
"značka pošlje na mesec na osebo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/optimize/gamification.rst:None
