msgid ""
"To set up lead enrichment in the *CRM* application, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`CRM app --> Configuration --> Settings`. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Lead Generation` section, tick the checkbox next "
"to :guilabel:`Lead Enrichment`, and select either :guilabel:`Enrich leads on "
"demand only` or :guilabel:`Enrich all leads automatically`. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Save` button to activate the changes."
msgstr ""

