#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:3
msgid "Pro-forma invoices"
msgstr "Predračuni"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:5
msgid ""
"A *pro-forma invoice* is an abridged or estimated invoice sent in advance of "
"a delivery of goods. It notes the kind and quantity of goods, their value, "
"and other important information, such as weight and transportation charges."
msgstr ""
"*Predračun* je skrajšan ali ocenjen račun, poslan pred dobavo blaga. Navaja "
"vrsto in količino blaga, njegovo vrednost in druge pomembne informacije, kot "
"so teža in stroški prevoza."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:9
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices are commonly used as preliminary invoices with a "
"quotation. They are also used during importation for customs purposes. They "
"differ from a normal invoice, in that they are *not* a demand (or request) "
"for payment."
msgstr ""
"Predračuni se običajno uporabljajo kot predhodni računi s ponudbo. "
"Uporabljajo se tudi pri uvozu za carinske namene. Razlikujejo se od "
"običajnega računa v tem, da *niso* zahteva (ali prošnja) za plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:16
msgid ""
"In order to utilize pro-forma invoices, the *Pro-Forma Invoice* feature "
"**must** be activated."
msgstr "Za uporabo predračunov *mora* biti aktivirana funkcija *Predračun*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:18
msgid ""
"To enable this feature, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`, and in the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& Orders` "
"section, click the checkbox next to :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr ""
"Za omogočitev te funkcije pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> "
"Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in v razdelku :guilabel:`Ponudbe in naročila` "
"kliknite potrditveno polje poleg :guilabel:`Predračun`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite vse spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid "The Pro-Forma Invoice feature setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Nastavitev funkcije predračuna v aplikaciji Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:27
msgid "Send pro-forma invoice"
msgstr "Pošlji predračun"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:29
msgid ""
"With the :guilabel:`Pro-Forma Invoice` feature activated, the option to send "
"a pro-forma invoice is now available on any quotation or sales order, via "
"the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button."
msgstr ""
"S funkcijo :guilabel:`Predračun` aktivirano je zdaj na voljo možnost "
"pošiljanja predračuna na katerem koli predračunu ali prodajnem nalogu prek "
"gumba :guilabel:`Pošlji predračun`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Send Pro-Forma Invoice button on a typical sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Gumb Pošlji predračun na običajnem prodajnem nalogu v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:37
msgid ""
"Pro-forma invoices can **not** be sent for a sales order or quotation if an "
"invoice for a down payment has already been sent, or for a recurring "
"subscription."
msgstr ""
"Predračunov **ni** mogoče pošiljati za prodajni nalog ali predračun, če je "
"bil že poslan račun za polog ali za ponavljajočo se naročnino."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:40
msgid ""
"In either case, the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Froma Invoice` button does **not** "
"appear."
msgstr "V obeh primerih se gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji predračun` **ne** prikaže."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:42
msgid ""
"However, pro-forma invoices **can** be sent for services, event "
"registrations, courses, and/or new subscriptions. Pro-forma invoices are not "
"limited to physical, consumable, or storable goods."
msgstr ""
"Vendar pa je predračune **mogoče** pošiljati za storitve, prijave na "
"dogodke, tečaje in/ali nove naročnine. Predračuni niso omejeni na fizično "
"blago, potrošni material ali blago za skladiščenje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:45
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`Send Pro-Forma Invoice` button is clicked, a pop-up "
"window appears, from which an email can be sent."
msgstr ""
"Ko kliknete gumb :guilabel:`Pošlji predračun`, se prikaže pojavno okno, iz "
"katerega lahko pošljete e-pošto."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:48
msgid ""
"In the pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Recipients` field is auto-populated "
"with the customer from the sales order or quotation. The :guilabel:`Subject` "
"field and the body of the email can be modified, if necessary."
msgstr ""
"V pojavnem oknu je polje :guilabel:`Prejemniki` samodejno izpolnjeno s "
"stranko iz prodajnega naloga ali predračuna. Polje :guilabel:`Zadeva` in "
"besedilo e-pošte lahko po potrebi spremenite."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:52
msgid ""
"The pro-forma invoice is automatically added as an attachment to the email."
msgstr "Predračun je samodejno dodan kot priloga e-pošti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:54
msgid ""
"When ready, click :guilabel:`Send`, and Odoo instantly sends the email, with "
"the attached pro-forma invoice, to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Pošlji` in Odoo takoj pošlje e-"
"pošto s priloženim predračunom stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:None
msgid ""
"The email pop-up window that appears with pro-forma invoice attached in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno e-pošte, ki se prikaže s priloženim predračunom v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:62
msgid ""
"To preview what the pro-forma invoice looks like, click on the PDF at the "
"bottom of the email pop-up window *before* clicking :guilabel:`Send`. When "
"clicked, the pro-forma invoice is downloaded instantly. Open that PDF to "
"view (and review) the pro-forma invoice."
msgstr ""
"Če želite predogledati, kako izgleda predračun, kliknite na PDF na dnu "
"pojavnega okna e-pošte *preden* kliknete :guilabel:`Pošlji`. Ko kliknete, se "
"predračun takoj prenese. Odprite ta PDF za ogled (in pregled) predračuna."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/proforma.rst:0
msgid "Sample pro-forma invoice PDF from Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Vzorec PDF predračuna iz Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:3
msgid "Invoicing based on time and materials"
msgstr "Izdajanje računov na podlagi časa in materiala"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:5
msgid ""
"Invoicing based on time and/or materials is typically used when accurately "
"estimating the size of a project isn't possible, or when the requirements of "
"a project may change."
msgstr ""
"Izdajanje računov na podlagi časa in/ali materiala se običajno uporablja, ko "
"natančna ocena obsega projekta ni mogoča ali ko se zahteve projekta lahko "
"spremenijo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is different from a fixed-price contract, when a customer agrees to pay "
"a specified total for the fulfillment of the contract---no matter what needs "
"to be paid to the employees, sub-contractors, vendors, suppliers, and so on."
msgstr ""
"To se razlikuje od pogodbe s fiksno ceno, ko se stranka strinja, da bo "
"plačala določen skupni znesek za izpolnitev pogodbe—ne glede na to, kaj je "
"treba plačati zaposlenim, podizvajalcem, prodajalcem, dobaviteljem itd."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:12
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* app can invoice for time and various other expenses (e.g. "
"transport, lodging), as well as purchases needed to fulfill an order."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo *Sales* lahko izdaja račune za čas in različne druge stroške "
"(npr. prevoz, nastańitev) ter nabave, potrebne za izpolnitev naročila."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:16
msgid "App and settings configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija aplikacije in nastavitev"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:18
msgid ""
"First, in order to accurately keep track of the progress of a project, the "
"Odoo *Project* and *Accounting* apps **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Najprej je treba za natančno sledenje napredka projekta namestiti aplikaciji "
"Odoo *Projekt* in *Računovodstvo*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:21
msgid ""
"To install the *Project* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Project` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where the "
"*Project* app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev aplikacije *Projekt* se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Glavna "
"nadzorna plošča Odoo --> Aplikacije`. Nato na strani :guilabel:`Aplikacije` "
"poiščite blok aplikacije :guilabel:`Projekt` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Aktiviraj`. Stran se samodejno osveži in se vrne na glavno "
"nadzorno ploščo Odoo, kjer je aplikacija *Projekt* zdaj na voljo za dostop."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:26
msgid "Repeat the same process to install the *Accounting* application."
msgstr "Ponovite enak postopek za namestitev aplikacije *Računovodstvo*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:28
msgid ""
"After installation, click the :guilabel:`Accounting` app icon from the main "
"Odoo dashboard, and navigate to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`. "
"On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, scroll down to the :guilabel:`Analytics` "
"section, and ensure the box next to :guilabel:`Analytic Accounting` is "
"checked."
msgstr ""
"Po namestitvi kliknite ikono aplikacije :guilabel:`Računovodstvo` na glavni "
"nadzorni plošči Odoo in se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`. Na strani :guilabel:`Nastavitve` se pomaknite navzdol do "
"razdelka :guilabel:`Analitika` in prepričajte se, da je polje ob "
":guilabel:`Analitično računovodstvo` označeno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How it looks to activate the Analytic Accounting setting in Odoo Accounting "
"Setting page."
msgstr ""
"Kako izgleda aktivacija nastavitve Analitično računovodstvo na strani "
"nastavitev Odoo računovodstva."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:37
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:43
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Save` to save all changes."
msgstr "Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`, da shranite vse spremembe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:39
msgid ""
"Then, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main dashboard --> Project app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. On the :guilabel:`Settings` page, in "
"the :guilabel:`Time Management` section, ensure the box beside "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` feature is checked."
msgstr ""
"Nato se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Glavna nadzorna plošča Odoo --> "
"Aplikacija Projekt --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. Na strani "
":guilabel:`Nastavitve`, v razdelku :guilabel:`Upravljanje časa`, se "
"prepričajte, da je polje ob funkciji :guilabel:`Časovnice` označeno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"What the Timesheets feature looks like on the Odoo Project settings page."
msgstr ""
"Kako izgleda funkcija Časovnice na strani nastavitev aplikacije Odoo Projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:52
msgid "Service product configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija izdelka storitve"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:54
msgid ""
"With the *Timesheets* feature activated in the *Project* app, it is now "
"possible to invoice for time spent on a project, but **only** when the "
"following product configurations have been made."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija *Časovnice* aktivirana v aplikaciji *Projekt*, je zdaj mogoče "
"izdajati račune za čas, porabljen za projekt, vendar **samo**, če so bile "
"izvedene naslednje konfiguracije izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:58
msgid ""
"Invoicing for time spent on a project is **only** possible with products "
"that have *Service* set as the *Product Type* on their product form."
msgstr ""
"Izdajanje računov za čas, porabljen za projekt, je **samo** mogoče z "
"izdelki, ki imajo kot *Vrsta izdelka* nastavljeno *Storitev* na obrazcu "
"izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:61
msgid ""
"To configure a service product, first navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Products`. On the :guilabel:`Products` page, select the "
"desired service product to be configured, or click :guilabel:`New` to create "
"a new product."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo izdelka storitve se najprej pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`. Na strani "
":guilabel:`Izdelki` izberite želeni izdelek storitve za konfiguracijo ali "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite nov izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:65
msgid ""
"From the product form, in the :guilabel:`General Information` tab, set "
"the :guilabel:`Product Type` to :guilabel:`Service`. Then, open the drop-"
"down menu in the :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` field, and "
"select :guilabel:`Based on Timesheets`."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu izdelka, v zavihku :guilabel:`Splošne informacije`, nastavite "
":guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka` na :guilabel:`Storitev`. Nato odprite spustni meni "
"v polju :guilabel:`Politika izdajanja računov` in izberite :guilabel:`Glede "
"na časovnice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:69
msgid ""
"Next, from the :guilabel:`Create on Order` drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Project \\& Task`. That setting indicates that, when a "
"sales order is created with this specific service product, a new project and "
"task is created in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Nato iz spustnega menija :guilabel:`Ustvari pri naročilu` izberite "
":guilabel:`Projekt in opravilo`. Ta nastavitev pomeni, da se ob ustvarjanju "
"prodajnega naloga s tem določenim izdelkom storitve v aplikaciji *Projekt* "
"ustvarita nov projekt in opravilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"The correct settings for Invoicing Policy and Create on Order fields for "
"service product."
msgstr ""
"Pravilne nastavitve za polji Politika izdajanja računov in Ustvari pri "
"naročilu za izdelek storitve."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:78
msgid ""
"The option :guilabel:`Task` can be chosen instead from the :guilabel:`Create "
"on Order` drop-down menu. If :guilabel:`Task` is chosen, select an existing "
"project that the task will appear in from :guilabel:`Project` field, which "
"only appears if :guilabel:`Task` is chosen in the :guilabel:`Create on "
"Order` field."
msgstr ""
"Iz spustnega menija :guilabel:`Ustvari pri naročilu` je mogoče namesto tega "
"izbrati možnost :guilabel:`Opravilo`. Če je izbrano :guilabel:`Opravilo`, v "
"polju :guilabel:`Projekt`, ki se prikaže samo, če je v polju "
":guilabel:`Ustvari pri naročilu` izbrano :guilabel:`Opravilo`, izberite "
"obstoječi projekt, v katerem se bo pojavilo opravilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:84
msgid "Add time spent to sales order"
msgstr "Dodajanje porabljenega časa prodajnemu nalogu"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:86
msgid ""
"After properly configuring a service product with the correct *Invoicing "
"Policy* and *Create on Order* options, it is possible to add time spent to a "
"sales order."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izdelek storitve pravilno konfiguriran s pravilnima možnostma "
"*Politika izdajanja računov* in *Ustvari pri naročilu*, je mogoče prodajnemu "
"nalogu dodati porabljeni čas."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:89
msgid ""
"To see that in action, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> New` to "
"open a blank quotation form. Then, proceed to add a :guilabel:`Customer`, "
"and in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a product`, and "
"select the properly :ref:`configured service product <sales/invoicing/"
"configured-service-product>` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz tega v praksi se pomaknite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Prodaja --> Novo`, da odprete prazen obrazec ponudbe. Nato dodajte "
":guilabel:`Stranko` in v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila` kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj izdelek` ter iz spustnega menija izberite :ref:`pravilno "
"konfiguriran izdelek storitve <sales/invoicing/configured-service-product>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:94
msgid "Next, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the order."
msgstr "Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da potrdite naročilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:96
msgid ""
"After confirming the sales order, two smart buttons appear at the top of the "
"order form: :guilabel:`Projects` and :guilabel:`Tasks`."
msgstr ""
"Po potrditvi prodajnega naloga se na vrhu obrazca naročila prikažeta dva "
"pametna gumba: :guilabel:`Projekti` in :guilabel:`Opravila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How the Projects and Tasks smart buttons look on a Sales Order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Kako izgledajo pametna gumba Projekti in Opravila na prodajnem nalogu v Odoo "
"Prodaji."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:103
msgid ""
"If the :guilabel:`Projects` smart button is clicked, it reveals the specific "
"project related to this sales order. If the :guilabel:`Tasks` smart button "
"is clicked, it reveals the specific project task related to this sales "
"order. Both are also accessible in the *Project* app."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete pametno tipko :guilabel:`Projekti`, se prikaže določen projekt, "
"povezan s tem prodajnim nalogom. Če kliknete pametno tipko "
":guilabel:`Opravila`, se prikaže določeno opravilo projekta, povezano s tem "
"prodajnim nalogom. Oba sta dostopna tudi v aplikaciji *Projekt*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:107
msgid ""
"In order to add time spent on a sales order, click the :guilabel:`Tasks` "
"smart button."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati porabljen čas za prodajni nalog, kliknite pametno tipko "
":guilabel:`Opravila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:109
msgid ""
"On the task form, select the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. From "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab, employees can be assigned to work on the "
"project, and the time they spend working on the task can be added by the "
"employees or by the person who created the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu opravila izberite zavihek :guilabel:`Časovnice`. V zavihku "
":guilabel:`Časovnice` je mogoče kadru dodeliti delo na projektu, zaposleni "
"ali oseba, ki je ustvarila prodajni nalog, pa lahko doda čas, ki ga porabijo "
"za delo na opravilu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:113
msgid ""
"To add an employee, and the time spent working on the task, "
"click :guilabel:`Add a line` in the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab. Then, select "
"the appropriate :guilabel:`Date` and :guilabel:`Employee`. There is also the "
"option to add a brief description of the work done during this time in "
"the :guilabel:`Description` column, but it's not required."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati kader in porabljen čas za delo na opravilu, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico` v zavihku :guilabel:`Časovnice`. Nato izberite "
"ustrezen :guilabel:`Datum` in :guilabel:`Kader`. Obstaja tudi možnost "
"dodajanja kratkega opisa opravljenega dela v tem času v stolpcu "
":guilabel:`Opis`, vendar ni obvezno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:118
msgid ""
"Lastly, enter the amount of time worked on the task in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` column, and click away to complete that line in "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje vnesite čas, porabljen za opravilo, v stolpec :guilabel:`Porabljene "
"ure` in kliknite stran, da dokončate to vrstico v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Časovnice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:122
msgid ""
"The time entered in the :guilabel:`Hours Spent` column is immediately "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Allocated Time` field (located near the top of "
"the task form) as a percentage, which reflects how much of the total "
"allocated work hours have been done so far."
msgstr ""
"Čas, vnešen v stolpec :guilabel:`Porabljene ure`, se takoj odraža v polju "
":guilabel:`Dodeljeni čas` (ob vrhu obrazca opravila) kot odstotek, ki "
"odraža, koliko skupnih dodeljenih delovnih ur je bilo doslej opravljenih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:126
msgid ""
"That same information is found as numerical hours in the :guilabel:`Hours "
"Spent` and :guilabel:`Remaining Hours` fields, located at the bottom of "
"the :guilabel:`Timesheets` tab."
msgstr ""
"Iste informacije so kot številčne ure na voljo v poljih "
":guilabel:`Porabljene ure` in :guilabel:`Preostale ure`, ki se nahajajo na "
"dnu zavihka :guilabel:`Časovnice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"How the Timesheets tab appears on a task form in Odoo Sales and Odoo Project."
msgstr ""
"Kako se zavihek Časovnice prikazuje na obrazcu opravila v Odoo Prodaja in "
"Odoo Projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:133
msgid ""
"Repeat this process for however many employees and hours have been worked on "
"the project."
msgstr ""
"Ta postopek ponovite za toliko zaposlenih in ur, kolikor jih je bilo "
"porabljenih za projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:136
msgid "Invoice time spent"
msgstr "Zaračunavanje porabljenega časa"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:138
msgid ""
"Once all the necessary employees and time spent have been added to the "
"project task, return to the sales order to invoice the customer for those "
"hours. To do that, either click the :guilabel:`Sales Order` smart button at "
"the top of the task form, or return to the sales order via the breadcrumb "
"links, located in the upper-left of the screen."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi potrebni zaposleni in porabljen čas dodani opravilu projekta, se "
"vrnite na prodajni nalog, da stranki zaračunate te ure. To storite tako, da "
"kliknete pametno tipko :guilabel:`Prodajni nalog` na vrhu obrazca opravila "
"ali se vrnete na prodajni nalog prek povezav za navigacijo v zgornjem levem "
"kotu zaslona."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:143
msgid ""
"Back on the sales order form, the time that was added to the task is "
"reflected in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab (in the :guilabel:`Delivered` "
"column) and in the new :guilabel:`Recorded Hours` smart button at the top of "
"the sales order."
msgstr ""
"Nazaj na obrazcu prodajnega naloga se čas, dodan opravilu, odraža v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Vrstice naloga` (v stolpcu :guilabel:`Dobavljeno`) in v novi "
"pametni tipki :guilabel:`Zabeležene ure` na vrhu prodajnega naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:147
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for time spent on the project, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, and select :guilabel:`Regular invoice` "
"from the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite stranki zaračunati čas, porabljen za projekt, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Ustvari račun` in v pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Ustvari račune` "
"izberite :guilabel:`Navaden račun`. Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari osnutek "
"računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:151
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft`, clearly showing all "
"the work that's been done in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"S tem se prikaže :guilabel:`Osnutek računa stranki`, ki jasno prikazuje vse "
"opravljeno delo v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:155
msgid ""
"Pay attention to the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column in "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Invoice`, as that information is necessary to ensure "
"other time/material invoicing tasks are completed properly and accurately."
msgstr ""
"Bodite pozorni na stolpec :guilabel:`Analitična porazdelitev` v "
":guilabel:`Računu stranki`, saj so te informacije potrebne za pravilno in "
"natančno dokončanje drugih opravil zaračunavanja časa/materiala."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid "Invoice draft showing time spent on sales order in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Osnutek računa, ki prikazuje porabljen čas za prodajni nalog v Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:163
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the invoice and continue with the "
"invoicing process."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da potrdite račun in nadaljujete s postopkom "
"zaračunavanja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:169
msgid "Expenses configuration"
msgstr "Nastavitev stroškov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:171
msgid ""
"In order to track and invoice expenses related to a sales order, the Odoo "
"*Expenses* app **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Za sledenje in zaračunavanje stroškov, povezanih s prodajnim nalogom, "
"**mora** biti nameščena aplikacija Odoo *Stroški*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:174
msgid ""
"To install the *Expenses* app, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Expenses` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite namestiti aplikacijo *Stroški*, se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`Glavna nadzorna plošča Odoo --> Aplikacije`. Nato na strani "
":guilabel:`Aplikacije` poiščite blok aplikacije :guilabel:`Stroški` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Aktiviraj`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:178
msgid ""
"The page automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, "
"where the :guilabel:`Expenses` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Stran se samodejno osveži in se vrne na glavno nadzorno ploščo Odoo, kjer je "
"zdaj na voljo aplikacija :guilabel:`Expenses`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:184
msgid "Add expenses to sales order"
msgstr "Dodaj stroške prodajnemu nalogu"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:186
msgid ""
"To add an expense to a sales order, first navigate to "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. Then, from the main *Expenses* dashboard, "
"click :guilabel:`New`, which reveals a blank expense form."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati strošek prodajnemu nalogu, najprej pojdite na aplikacijo "
":menuselection:`Expenses`. Nato na glavni nadzorni plošči *Expenses* "
"kliknite :guilabel:`New`, kar prikaže prazen obrazec za stroške."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:189
msgid ""
"On the expense form, add a :guilabel:`Description` of the expense (e.g. "
"`Hotel Stay`, `Plane Ticket`). Next, in the :guilabel:`Category` field, "
"select the appropriate option from the drop-down menu "
"(e.g. :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, :guilabel:`Travel \\& "
"Accommodation`)."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu za stroške dodajte :guilabel:`Description` stroška (npr. `Hotel "
"Stay`, `Plane Ticket`). Nato v polju :guilabel:`Category` izberite ustrezno "
"možnost iz spustnega menija (npr. :guilabel:`Meals`, :guilabel:`Miles`, "
":guilabel:`Travel \\& Accommodation`)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:194
msgid ""
"Expense categories can be added and modified by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."
msgstr ""
"Kategorije stroškov lahko dodate in spremenite tako, da pojdete na "
":menuselection:`Expenses app --> Configuration --> Expense Categories`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:197
msgid ""
"Then, enter the total amount of the expense in the :guilabel:`Total` field, "
"as well as any :guilabel:`Included Taxes` that may apply. Next, ensure that "
"the correct :guilabel:`Employee` is selected, and designate who paid for the "
"expense in the :guilabel:`Paid By` field: the :guilabel:`Employee (to "
"reimburse)` or the :guilabel:`Company`."
msgstr ""
"Nato vnesite skupni znesek stroška v polje :guilabel:`Total` ter morebitne "
":guilabel:`Included Taxes`, ki se lahko uporabijo. Nato se prepričajte, da "
"je izbran pravilen :guilabel:`Employee`, in določite, kdo je plačal strošek "
"v polju :guilabel:`Paid By`: :guilabel:`Employee (to reimburse)` ali "
":guilabel:`Company`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:202
msgid ""
"Next, in the :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` field, select the appropriate "
"sales order from the drop-down menu. Then, select that same sales order "
"information from the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field, as well."
msgstr ""
"Nato v polju :guilabel:`Customer to Reinvoice` izberite ustrezni prodajni "
"nalog iz spustnega menija. Nato izberite enake informacije prodajnega naloga "
"tudi v polju :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:207
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field will **only** have the "
"corresponding sales order as an option if the sales order contains a service "
"product that is billed based on *Timesheets*, *Milestones*, or *Delivered "
"Quantities*."
msgstr ""
"Polje :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` bo imelo ustrezen prodajni nalog kot "
"možnost **samo**, če prodajni nalog vsebuje storitev, ki se zaračunava na "
"podlagi *Timesheets*, *Milestones* ali *Delivered Quantities*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to properly fill out an expense form that's attached to a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kako pravilno izpolniti obrazec za stroške, ki je priložen prodajnemu nalogu "
"v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:215
msgid ""
"If there are any receipts that should be uploaded and attached to the "
"expense, click the :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` button, and upload the "
"necessary documents to the expense. This is **not** required, but it may "
"affect whether or not an expense is approved."
msgstr ""
"Če obstajajo računi, ki bi jih bilo treba naložiti in priložiti strošku, "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Attach Receipt` in naložite potrebne dokumente k "
"strošku. To **ni** obvezno, vendar lahko vpliva na to, ali bo strošek "
"odobren ali ne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:219
msgid ""
"When all the information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Create Report` "
"to create an expense report detailing all the expense information that was "
"just entered."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vneseni vsi podatki, kliknite :guilabel:`Create Report`, da ustvarite "
"poročilo o stroških s podrobnostmi o vseh pravkar vnesenih informacijah o "
"strošku."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid "How an Expense Report Summary looks in Odoo Expenses."
msgstr "Kako izgleda povzetek poročila o stroških v Odoo Expenses."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:226
msgid ""
"Then, there's the option to :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` for approval. Once "
"approved, the :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip` appears."
msgstr ""
"Nato je na voljo možnost :guilabel:`Submit to Manager` za odobritev. Po "
"odobritvi se prikaže :guilabel:`Report in Next Payslip`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:229
msgid ""
"To showcase a complete flow in this example, select :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Then, the manager would click :guilabel:`Approve` to approve this "
"expense, and click :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries` to post this expense to "
"the accounting journal."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz celotnega poteka v tem primeru izberite :guilabel:`Submit to "
"Manager`. Nato bi vodja kliknil :guilabel:`Approve`, da odobri ta strošek, "
"in kliknil :guilabel:`Post Journal Entries`, da objavi ta strošek v "
"računovodski dnevnik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:234
msgid "Invoice expenses"
msgstr "Zaračunaj stroške"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:236
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for an :ref:`expense on a sales order <sales/invoicing/"
"add-expenses-sales-order>`, navigate to the related sales order, either from "
"the :menuselection:`Sales` app or from the expense report in "
"the :menuselection:`Expenses` app. From the expense report, click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales Orders` smart button at the top of the page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite stranki zaračunati :ref:`expense on a sales order <sales/invoicing/"
"add-expenses-sales-order>`, pojdite na povezani prodajni nalog bodisi iz "
"aplikacije :menuselection:`Sales` bodisi iz poročila o stroških v aplikaciji "
":menuselection:`Expenses`. Iz poročila o stroških kliknite pametni gumb "
":guilabel:`Sales Orders` na vrhu strani."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:241
msgid ""
"If the expense report was linked to the sales order, the newly-configured "
"expense now has its own line in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, and can be "
"invoiced to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Če je bilo poročilo o stroških povezano s prodajnim nalogom, ima na novo "
"konfiguriran strošek svojo vrstico v zavihku :guilabel:`Order Lines` in ga "
"je mogoče zaračunati stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"An expense appearing on Order Lines tab of a Sales Order in Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr ""
"Strošek, ki se prikaže v zavihku Order Lines prodajnega naloga v aplikaciji "
"Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:248
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the expense on the sales order, "
"click :guilabel:`Create Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from "
"the :guilabel:`Create invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create "
"Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite stranki zaračunati strošek na prodajnem nalogu, kliknite "
":guilabel:`Create Invoice`, izberite :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` v pojavnem "
"oknu :guilabel:`Create invoices` in nato kliknite :guilabel:`Create Draft "
"Invoice`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:252
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` for the expense. Then, "
"the invoicing process can be completed as usual."
msgstr ""
"S tem se prikaže :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` za strošek. Nato lahko "
"proces fakturiranja dokončate kot običajno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample customer invoice for an expense generated from a sales order in Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Vzorčni račun stranki za strošek, ustvarjen iz prodajnega naloga v Odoo "
"Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:260
msgid "Purchase configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija nabave"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:262
msgid ""
"In order to invoice a customer for purchases made on a sales order, the "
"*Purchase* application **must** be installed."
msgstr ""
"Da bi stranki zaračunali nakupe iz prodajnega naloga, **mora** biti "
"nameščena aplikacija *Purchase*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:265
msgid ""
"To install the *Purchase* application, navigate to :menuselection:`Odoo main "
"dashboard --> Apps`. Then, on the :guilabel:`Apps` page, locate "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app block, and click :guilabel:`Activate`. The page "
"automatically refreshes and returns to the main Odoo dashboard, where "
"the :guilabel:`Purchase` app is now available to access."
msgstr ""
"Za namestitev aplikacije *Purchase* pojdite na :menuselection:`Glavna "
"nadzorna plošča Odoo --> Aplikacije`. Nato na strani :guilabel:`Aplikacije` "
"poiščite blok aplikacije :guilabel:`Purchase` in kliknite "
":guilabel:`Aktiviraj`. Stran se samodejno osveži in vrne na glavno nadzorno "
"ploščo Odoo, kjer je zdaj na voljo aplikacija :guilabel:`Purchase`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:273
msgid "Add purchase to sales order"
msgstr "Dodaj nabavo k prodajnemu nalogu"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:275
msgid ""
"To add a purchase to a sales order, a purchase order must first be created. "
"To create a purchase order, navigate to :menuselection:`Purchase app --> "
"New` to reveal a blank purchase order form."
msgstr ""
"Da bi dodali nabavo k prodajnemu nalogu, morate najprej ustvariti nabavni "
"nalog. Za ustvaritev nabavnega naloga pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Purchase --> Nov`, da se prikaže prazen obrazec nabavnega naloga."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:278
msgid ""
"First, add a :guilabel:`Vendor` to the purchase order. Then, under "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`extra column options` "
"drop-down menu, represented by two horizontal lines with dots on them, "
"located to the far-right of the column headers. From that drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution`."
msgstr ""
"Najprej dodajte :guilabel:`Dobavitelja` k nabavnemu nalogu. Nato v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Izdelki` kliknite spustni meni :guilabel:`dodatne možnosti "
"stolpcev`, ki ga predstavljata dve vodoravni črti s pikami, na skrajni desni "
"strani glav stolpcev. Iz tega spustnega menija izberite "
":guilabel:`Analitična porazdelitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to add analytic distribution column on purchase order form in Odoo "
"Purchase."
msgstr ""
"Kako dodati stolpec analitične porazdelitve na obrazec nabavnega naloga v "
"Odoo Purchase."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:287
msgid ""
"After adding the :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` column to the headers on "
"the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the purchase order form, proceed to add the "
"product(s) to the purchase order. To do that, click :guilabel:`Add a "
"product`, and select the desired product from the drop-down menu. Repeat for "
"all the products to add."
msgstr ""
"Ko dodate stolpec :guilabel:`Analitična porazdelitev` k glavam v zavihku "
":guilabel:`Izdelki` obrazca nabavnega naloga, nadaljujte z dodajanjem "
"izdelkov k nabavnemu nalogu. To storite tako, da kliknete :guilabel:`Dodaj "
"izdelek` in iz spustnega menija izberete želeni izdelek. Ponovite za vse "
"izdelke, ki jih želite dodati."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:293
msgid ""
"In order for a purchase to be properly invoiced on a sales order, the "
"product on the purchase order **must** be marked as :guilabel:`Can be "
"Expensed`, have an :guilabel:`Invoicing Policy` set to :guilabel:`Delivered "
"quantities`, and have the :guilabel:`At cost` option selected in "
"the :guilabel:`Re-Invoice Expenses` field on its product form."
msgstr ""
"Da bi bil nakup pravilno zaračunan na prodajnem nalogu, **mora** biti "
"izdelek na nabavnem nalogu označen kot :guilabel:`Lahko stroškovno knjižen`, "
"imeti :guilabel:`Pravila fakturiranja` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Dobavljene "
"količine` in imeti izbrano možnost :guilabel:`Po nabavni ceni` v polju "
":guilabel:`Ponovno zaračunaj stroške` na njegovem obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:0
msgid ""
"Product settings for a purchase order to be invoiced on a sales order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitve izdelka, da se nabavni nalog zaračuna na prodajnem nalogu v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:302
msgid ""
"Then, select the appropriate :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` associated "
"with the sales order to which this purchase order is related. To do that, "
"click the empty :guilabel:`Analytic Distribution` field to reveal "
"an :guilabel:`Analytic` pop-up window."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite ustrezno :guilabel:`Analitično porazdelitev`, povezano s "
"prodajnim nalogom, na katerega se nanaša ta nabavni nalog. To storite tako, "
"da kliknete prazno polje :guilabel:`Analitična porazdelitev`, da se prikaže "
"pojavno okno :guilabel:`Analitika`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:306
msgid ""
"Then, from the :guilabel:`Departments` drop-down menu, select the analytic "
"distribution associated with the desired sales order to be invoiced for the "
"purchase."
msgstr ""
"Nato iz spustnega menija :guilabel:`Oddelki` izberite analitično "
"porazdelitev, povezano z želenim prodajnim nalogom, ki bo zaračunan za nakup."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to select the Analytic Distribution department from a purchase order in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Kako izbrati oddelek analitične porazdelitve iz nabavnega naloga v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:313
msgid ""
"Once all the information is entered in the :guilabel:`Products` tab of the "
"purchase order, confirm the order by clicking :guilabel:`Confirm Order`. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Receive Products` when the products have been "
"received. This creates a receipt form."
msgstr ""
"Ko so vsi podatki vneseni v zavihek :guilabel:`Izdelki` nabavnega naloga, "
"potrdite nalog s klikom na :guilabel:`Potrdi nalog`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Prejmi izdelke`, ko so izdelki prejeti. To ustvari obrazec "
"prejema."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:318
msgid ""
"If any serial/lot numbers must be entered before validating the receipt of "
"products, then on the receipt form, click the :guilabel:`details` icon "
"represented by four horizontal lines located to the far-right of the product "
"line."
msgstr ""
"Če je treba vnesti kakršne koli serijske/šaržne številke pred potrditvijo "
"prejema izdelkov, potem na obrazcu prejema kliknite ikono "
":guilabel:`podrobnosti`, ki jo predstavljajo štiri vodoravne črte na skrajni "
"desni strani vrstice izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:322
msgid ""
"This reveals a :guilabel:`Detailed Operations` tab, in which the "
"necessary :guilabel:`Lot/Serial Number(s)` and :guilabel:`Done` quantity can "
"be added. When ready, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the data."
msgstr ""
"To prikaže zavihek :guilabel:`Podrobne operacije`, v katerem lahko dodate "
"potrebne :guilabel:`Šaržne/serijske številke` in količino "
":guilabel:`Opravljeno`. Ko ste pripravljeni, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da "
"potrdite podatke."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:326
msgid "Then, click :guilabel:`Validate` to validate the purchase order."
msgstr "Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da potrdite nabavni nalog."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:328
msgid ""
"Next, return to the purchase order, via the breadcrumb links at the top of "
"the page, and click :guilabel:`Create Bill` to create a vendor bill that can "
"be invoiced to the customer on the attached sales order."
msgstr ""
"Nato se vrnite na nabavni nalog prek povezav za navigacijo na vrhu strani in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari račun`, da ustvarite dobaviteljev račun, ki ga "
"lahko zaračunate stranki na priloženem prodajnem nalogu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Vendor bill draft for a purchase order to be invoiced to a customer in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Osnutek dobaviteljevega računa za nabavni nalog, ki bo zaračunan stranki v "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:337
msgid ""
"Make sure to enter a :guilabel:`Bill Date` on the :guilabel:`Vendor Bill "
"Draft` before confirming. If a :guilabel:`Bill Date` is *not* entered, an "
"error window appears, requesting that information to be entered before "
"confirmation can occur."
msgstr ""
"Pred potrditvijo se prepričajte, da ste v :guilabel:`Osnutek dobaviteljevega "
"računa` vnesli :guilabel:`Datum računa`. Če :guilabel:`Datum računa` *ni* "
"vnešen, se prikaže okno z napako, ki zahteva vnos te informacije pred "
"potrditvijo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:341
msgid ""
"Then, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the vendor bill, which is then "
"automatically added to the sales order, where it can be invoiced directly to "
"the customer attached to it."
msgstr ""
"Nato kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, da potrdite dobaviteljev račun, ki se nato "
"samodejno doda k prodajnemu nalogu, kjer ga je mogoče neposredno izdati v "
"račun stranki, povezani z njim."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:345
msgid "Invoice purchase"
msgstr "Zaračunaj nakup"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:347
msgid ""
"To invoice a customer for a purchase on a sales order, first :ref:`add the "
"purchase to the sales order <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-sales-order>`, "
"then navigate to the desired sales order in the :menuselection:`Sales` app."
msgstr ""
"Če želite stranki zaračunati nakup na prodajnem nalogu, najprej "
":ref:`dodajte nakup k prodajnemu nalogu <sales/invoicing/add-purchase-to-"
"sales-order>`, nato pa se pomaknite do želenega prodajnega naloga v "
"aplikaciji :menuselection:`Sales`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:351
msgid ""
"On the sales order that was attached to the purchase order, the purchased "
"product now has its own product line under the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab, "
"and it is ready to be invoiced."
msgstr ""
"Na prodajnem nalogu, ki je bil povezan z nabavnim nalogom, ima kupljeni "
"izdelek zdaj svojo vrstico pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila` in je "
"pripravljen za izdajo računa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Purchase order product on sales order to be invoiced to customer via Odoo "
"Sales."
msgstr ""
"Izdelek iz nabavnega naloga na prodajnem nalogu, ki se zaračuna stranki prek "
"Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:358
msgid ""
"To invoice the customer for the purchase, simply click :guilabel:`Create "
"Invoice`, select :guilabel:`Regular Invoice` from the :guilabel:`Create "
"invoices` pop-up window, then click :guilabel:`Create Draft Invoice`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite stranki zaračunati nakup, preprosto kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari "
"račun`, izberite :guilabel:`Običajni račun` iz pojavnega okna "
":guilabel:`Ustvari račune`, nato pa kliknite :guilabel:`Ustvari osnutek "
"računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:362
msgid ""
"Doing so reveals a :guilabel:`Customer Invoice Draft` with the newly-added "
"purchase order product in the :guilabel:`Invoice Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"S tem se prikaže :guilabel:`Osnutek računa stranki` z novo dodanim izdelkom "
"iz nabavnega naloga v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice računa`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:None
msgid ""
"Customer invoice draft with purchase product attached to sales order in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Osnutek računa stranki z izdelkom iz nabave, povezanim s prodajnim nalogom v "
"Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:369
msgid ""
"To complete the invoicing process, click :guilabel:`Confirm` to confirm the "
"invoice, and then click :guilabel:`Register Payment` in "
"the :guilabel:`Register Payment` pop-up form."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dokončati postopek izdajanja računa, kliknite :guilabel:`Potrdi`, "
"da potrdite račun, nato pa kliknite :guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo` v "
"obrazcu :guilabel:`Registriraj plačilo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices.rst:5
msgid "Products & Prices"
msgstr "Izdelki in cene"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:3
msgid "Use eWallets and gift cards"
msgstr "Uporaba e-denarnic in darilnih kartic"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:5
msgid ""
"With Odoo, customers can use **eWallets** and **gift cards** for online and "
"in-store shopping."
msgstr ""
"Z Odoo lahko stranke uporabljajo **e-denarnice** in **darilne kartice** za "
"spletno in fizično nakupovanje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:7
msgid ""
"To enable eWallets and gift cards for eCommerce and Point of Sale (PoS), "
"first enable :guilabel:`Discounts, Loyalty & Gift Card` "
"under :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings --> Pricing "
"section`. Once enabled, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Gift cards & eWallet` and :guilabel:`Create` a new eWallet or gift card "
"program."
msgstr ""
"Če želite omogočiti e-denarnice in darilne kartice za eCommerce in prodajno "
"točko (PoS), najprej omogočite :guilabel:`Popusti, zvestoba in darilne "
"kartice` pod :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve --> razdelek Cene`. Ko je omogočeno, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Izdelki --> Darilne kartice in e-"
"denarnica` in :guilabel:`Ustvari` nov program e-denarnice ali darilne "
"kartice."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:13
msgid "eWallets"
msgstr "e-denarnice"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:15
msgid ""
"eWallets allow customers to save credits on their online account and use "
"these credits as a payment method when buying items in an online store or a "
"brick-and-mortar store. eWallets can also be used to centralize "
"multiple :ref:`gift cards <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."
msgstr ""
"e-Denarnice strankam omogočajo shranjevanje dobroimetja na njihovem spletnem "
"računu in uporabo tega dobroimetja kot način plačila pri nakupu artiklov v "
"spletni trgovini ali fizični trgovini. e-Denarnice je mogoče uporabiti tudi "
"za centralizacijo več :ref:`darilnih kartic <ewallet_gift/gift-cards>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:19
msgid ""
"Before creating an eWallet program, it is necessary to create an eWallet "
"**top-up** product. Top-ups are pre-defined digital credit values added to "
"an eWallet in exchange for its equivalent in real currency. These credits "
"can then be used as a payment method in the eCommerce shop or :abbr:`PoS "
"(Point of Sale)`. Top-up values can be of different amounts."
msgstr ""
"Pred ustvarjanjem programa e-denarnice je treba ustvariti izdelek za "
"**dopolnitev** e-denarnice. Dopolnitve so vnaprej določene vrednosti "
"digitalnega dobroimetja, dodanega e-denarnici v zameno za njegov ekvivalent "
"v pravi valuti. To dobroimetje je nato mogoče uporabiti kot način plačila v "
"spletni trgovini ali :abbr:`PoS (prodajni točki)`. Vrednosti dopolnitev so "
"lahko različnih zneskov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:25
msgid ""
"A $50 top-up can be bought for $50, and adds that same amount of credits to "
"the eWallet."
msgstr ""
"Dopolnitev za 50 $ je mogoče kupiti za 50 $ in doda enak znesek dobroimetja "
"v e-denarnico."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:27
msgid ""
"To create a top-up product, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> "
"Products` and :guilabel:`Create` a new product. On the product template, "
"configure the options as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti izdelek za dopolnitev, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Izdelki --> Izdelki` in "
":guilabel:`Ustvari` nov izdelek. V predlogi izdelka konfigurirajte možnosti "
"na naslednji način:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:30
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Product Name`: enter a name for the top-up product (for example, "
"`$50 Top-Up`)"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ime izdelka`: vnesite ime za izdelek dopolnitve (na primer "
"`Dopolnitev za 50 $`)"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:31
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:92
msgid ":guilabel:`Can be Sold`: enabled"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Lahko se proda`: omogočeno"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:32
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/products_prices/ewallets_giftcards.rst:93
msgid ":guilabel:`Product Type`: select :guilabel:`Service`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vrsta izdelka`: izberite :guilabel:`Storitev`"

