#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:3
msgid "Custom email signatures"
msgstr "Prilagojeni podpisi e-pošte"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:5
msgid ""
"Some business workflows require email template signatures to be updated so "
"outgoing communications display the appropriate contact information for "
"customer follow-up and correspondence."
msgstr ""
"Nekateri poslovni procesi zahtevajo posodobitev podpisov predlog e-pošte, "
"tako da odhodne komunikacije prikazujejo ustrezne kontaktne informacije za "
"nadaljnje delo s strankami in korespondenco."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is particularly important when responsibility for a customer "
"opportunity is shared between team members. In these cases, the employee "
"responsible for managing quotes and customer communications may differ from "
"the employee associated with the sales order for commission purposes."
msgstr ""
"To je še posebej pomembno, ko si člani ekipe delijo odgovornost za "
"priložnost s stranko. V teh primerih se lahko kader, odgovoren za "
"upravljanje ponudb in komunikacije s strankami, razlikuje od kadra, "
"povezanega s prodajnim nalogom za namene provizije."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:12
msgid ""
"Email templates default to the signature of the employee assigned to the "
"record; therefore the template should be modified to display the contact "
"information of the employee responsible for customer follow-up. This ensures "
"customers know who to contact with questions, approvals, and other "
"correspondence."
msgstr ""
"Predloge e-pošte privzeto uporabljajo podpis kadra, dodeljenega zapisu; zato "
"je treba predlogo spremeniti, da prikazuje kontaktne informacije kadra, "
"odgovornega za nadaljnje delo s strankami. To zagotavlja, da stranke vedo, s "
"kom se obrniti v zvezi z vprašanji, odobritvami in drugo korespondenco."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:18
msgid ""
"The `Sales: Order Confirmation` email template is used as the example "
"throughout this article to demonstrate how email signatures can be "
"customized."
msgstr ""
"Predloga e-pošte `Sales: Order Confirmation` se uporablja kot primer v tem "
"članku za prikaz, kako lahko prilagodite podpise e-pošte."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:22
msgid "Open the email template"
msgstr "Odprite predlogo e-pošte"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:24
msgid ""
"To modify an email template, first :ref:`activate developer mode <developer-"
"mode/activation>`, then navigate to :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"Technical --> Email Templates`. Click on the email template being modified, "
"in this case, the `Sales: Order Confirmation` template."
msgstr ""
"Za spreminjanje predloge e-pošte najprej :ref:`aktivirajte razvijalski način "
"<developer-mode/activation>`, nato se pomaknite na "
":menuselection:`aplikacija Nastavitve --> Tehnično --> Predloge e-pošte`. "
"Kliknite na predlogo e-pošte, ki jo spreminjate, v tem primeru predlogo "
"`Sales: Order Confirmation`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:29
msgid "Update from field"
msgstr "Posodobite polje od"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:31
msgid ""
"On the email template, open the *Email Configuration* tab. Delete the "
"default text in the :guilabel:`From` field and replace it with: "
"`{{ (user.email_formatted) }}`."
msgstr ""
"V predlogi e-pošte odprite zavihek *Konfiguracija e-pošte*. Izbrišite "
"privzeto besedilo v polju :guilabel:`Od` in ga zamenjajte z: `{{ "
"(user.email_formatted) }}`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:None
msgid "The from field updated with the correct text."
msgstr "Polje od je posodobljeno s pravilnim besedilom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:38
msgid "Modify the code"
msgstr "Spremenite kodo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:40
msgid ""
"Click the *Content* tab, and highlight some text so the toolbar is visible. "
"Click the :guilabel:`</> (Code view)` button and the text changes to code."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite zavihek *Vsebina* in označite besedilo, da bo orodna vrstica vidna. "
"Kliknite gumb :guilabel:`</> (Pogled s kodo)` in besedilo se spremeni v kodo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:43
msgid ""
"Search the code for `signature` to find the two instances of the code "
"`object.user_id.signature`. Replace both `object.user_id.signature` "
"instances with `User.signature`."
msgstr ""
"V kodi poiščite `signature`, da najdete dva primera kode "
"`object.user_id.signature`. Zamenjajte oba primera "
"`object.user_id.signature` z `User.signature`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:None
msgid ""
"The two 'object.user_id.signature' fields replaced with 'User.signature'."
msgstr "Polji 'object.user_id.signature' sta zamenjani z 'User.signature'."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:50
msgid ""
"If a user has not set up their email signature, instead of having the "
"default `Mitchell Admin` populate the signature, the company name can be "
"displayed instead."
msgstr ""
"Če uporabnik ni nastavil svojega podpisa e-pošte, se namesto privzetega "
"`Mitchell Admin`, ki izpolni podpis, lahko prikaže ime podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/custom_signatures.rst:53
msgid ""
"To do this, search for `Mitchell Admin` in the code, and replace it with the "
"company name."
msgstr ""
"Za to v kodi poiščite `Mitchell Admin` in ga zamenjajte z imenom podjetja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:3
msgid "Quotation deadlines"
msgstr "Roki ponudb"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:5
msgid ""
"In the Odoo *Sales* application, it is possible to set deadlines on sales "
"quotations. Doing so encourages customers to act quickly during sales "
"negotiations, for they might fear for missing out on a good deal. As well, "
"deadlines also can also act as protection for a company in case an order has "
"to be fulfilled at a price that is no longer profitable for the business."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Odoo *Prodaja* je mogoče nastaviti roke za prodajne ponudbe. S "
"tem spodbudite stranke, da hitro ukrepajo med prodajnimi pogajanji, saj bi "
"lahko zamudile dobro ponudbo. Poleg tega lahko roki služijo tudi kot zaščita "
"za podjetje v primeru, da je treba naročilo izpolniti po ceni, ki za "
"podjetje ni več donosna."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:11
msgid "Quotation expiration"
msgstr "Potek veljavnosti ponudbe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:13
msgid ""
"In Odoo *Sales*, there's the option to add an expiration date to a quotation."
msgstr ""
"V Odoo *Prodaja* obstaja možnost dodajanja datuma poteka veljavnosti ponudbi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:15
msgid ""
"To add an expiration date to a quotation, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales "
"app`, and select a desired quotation, or create a new one by "
"clicking :guilabel:`New`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ponudbi dodati datum poteka, pojdite na :menuselection:`Prodaja` "
"in izberite želeno ponudbo ali ustvarite novo s klikom na :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:18
msgid ""
"On the quotation form, click the :guilabel:`Expiration` field to reveal a "
"pop-up calendar. From this pop-up calendar, select the desired month and "
"date as the expiration date for the quotation."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu ponudbe kliknite polje :guilabel:`Potek`, da se prikaže pojavni "
"koledar. V tem pojavnem koledarju izberite želeni mesec in datum kot datum "
"poteka ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:None
msgid "The expiration field on a standard quotation form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Polje za potek na standardnem obrazcu ponudbe v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:26
msgid ""
"By clicking the :guilabel:`Preview` button on a quotation, Odoo clearly "
"displays when that specific offer expires."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na gumb :guilabel:`Predogled` na ponudbi Odoo jasno prikaže, kdaj "
"ta ponudba poteče."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:0
msgid "How customers will see deadlines on Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Kako bodo stranke videle roke v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:34
msgid "Quotation template expiration"
msgstr "Potek predloge ponudbe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:36
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* application also makes it possible to add a deadline "
"expiration date to quotation templates."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo *Sales* omogoča tudi dodajanje roka poteka predlogam ponudb."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:39
msgid ""
"To add a deadline expiration date to a quotation template, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Quotation Templates`, and "
"either select the desired quotation template to which a deadline should be "
"added, or click :guilabel:`New` to build a new quotation template from "
"scratch."
msgstr ""
"Če želite predlogi ponudbe dodati rok poteka, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Predloge ponudb` in izberite "
"želeno predlogo ponudbe, ki ji želite dodati rok, ali kliknite "
":guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite novo predlogo ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:43
msgid ""
"On the quotation template form, add a specific number of days to "
"the :guilabel:`Quotation expires after` field, located beneath the quotation "
"template name. The number of days represents how long the quotation will be "
"valid for, before it expires."
msgstr ""
"Na obrazcu predloge ponudbe dodajte določeno število dni v polje "
":guilabel:`Ponudba poteče po`, ki se nahaja pod imenom predloge ponudbe. "
"Število dni predstavlja, kako dolgo bo ponudba veljavna, preden poteče."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:None
msgid ""
"The quotation expires after field on a quotation template form in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Polje za potek ponudbe na obrazcu predloge ponudbe v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/deadline.rst:51
msgid ""
"Then, whenever that specific quotation template is used in a quote, an "
"expiration date is automatically calculated, based on the number of days "
"designated above. However, this date can be overwritten before sending the "
"quotation to the customer."
msgstr ""
"Ko se ta predloga ponudbe uporabi v ponudbi, se datum poteka samodejno "
"izračuna na podlagi zgoraj navedenega števila dni. Ta datum pa je mogoče "
"spremeniti, preden se ponudba pošlje stranki."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:3
msgid "Deliveries and invoices to different addresses"
msgstr "Dostave in računi na različne naslove"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:5
msgid ""
"People and businesses often use separate addresses for billing (invoicing) "
"and shipping (delivery) purposes. With the Odoo **Sales** app, contacts can "
"have different specified addresses for delivery and invoicing."
msgstr ""
"Ljudje in podjetja pogosto uporabljajo ločene naslove za fakturiranje in "
"dostavo. Z aplikacijo Odoo **Sales** lahko imajo stiki različne določene "
"naslove za dostavo in fakturiranje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:12
msgid ""
"To properly utilize multiple addresses in Odoo, go to "
"the :menuselection:`Accounting app --> Configuration --> Settings`, and "
"scroll down to the :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` heading. Then, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Customer Addresses` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Za pravilno uporabo več naslovov v Odooju pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Računovodstvo --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se "
"pomaknite navzdol do naslova :guilabel:`Računi kupcev`. Nato označite "
"potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Naslovi kupcev`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:None
msgid "Activate the Customer Addresses setting."
msgstr "Aktivirajte nastavitev Naslovi strank."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:22
msgid "Contact form configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija obrazca za stik"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:24
msgid ""
"To add multiple addresses to a contact, go to the :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Orders --> Customers`, and clear any default filters from the search "
"bar. Then, click on the desired customer to open their contact form."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje več naslovov stiku pojdite v :menuselection:`Sales --> "
"Naročila --> Kupci` in počistite vse privzete filtre iz iskalne vrstice. "
"Nato kliknite na želenega kupca, da odprete njegov obrazec stika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:29
msgid "Contact forms can be accessed in the **Contacts** application, as well."
msgstr "Do obrazcev stikov je mogoče dostopati tudi v aplikaciji **Contacts**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:31
msgid ""
"From the contact form, click the :guilabel:`Add` button, which is located "
"under the :guilabel:`Contacts & Addresses` tab. This brings up "
"the :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form, in which additional addresses "
"can be configured."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:None
msgid "Add a contact/address to the contact form."
msgstr "Dodajte stik/naslov v obrazec za stik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:38
msgid ""
"On the :guilabel:`Create Contact` pop-up form, select any of the following "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Na pojavnem obrazcu :guilabel:`Ustvari stik` izberite katero koli od "
"naslednjih možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:40
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contact`: Adds another contact, such as an employee at a company, "
"to the contact form."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Stik`: doda drug stik, kot je zaposleni v podjetju, k obrazcu "
"stika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:41
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Invoice Address`: Adds a default invoice address to the contact "
"form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:42
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Delivery Address`: Adds a default delivery address to the contact "
"form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:43
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Follow-up Address`: Adds a default contact address that is used "
"for follow-up communications about billing and other issues to the contact "
"form."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:45
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other Address`: Adds an alternate address to the contact form."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Drugi naslov`: doda nadomestni naslov k obrazcu stika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:None
msgid "Create a new contact/address on a contact form."
msgstr "Ustvarite nov stik/naslov na obrazcu za stik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:50
msgid ""
"Once the corresponding information has been entered, click :guilabel:`Save & "
"Close` to save the address and close the :guilabel:`Create Contact` window. "
"To save the address and input additional contact information, "
"click :guilabel:`Save & New` instead."
msgstr ""
"Ko so ustrezne informacije vnesene, kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`, da "
"shranite naslov in zaprete okno :guilabel:`Ustvari stik`. Za shranitev "
"naslova in vnos dodatnih podatkov o stiku namesto tega kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani in novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:55
msgid "Quotations and autopopulated addresses"
msgstr "Ponudbe in samodejno izpolnjeni naslovi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:57
msgid ""
"When a customer with invoice and delivery addresses in their contact form is "
"added to a quotation, the :guilabel:`Invoice Address` "
"and :guilabel:`Delivery Address` fields autopopulate with the corresponding "
"addresses."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kupec z naslovi za račun in dostavo v svojem obrazcu stika dodan v "
"ponudbo, se polji :guilabel:`Naslov za račun` in :guilabel:`Naslov za "
"dostavo` samodejno izpolnita z ustreznimi naslovi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:None
msgid "Invoice and Delivery Addresses autopopulate on a quotation."
msgstr "Naslovi za račun in dostavo se samodejno izpolnijo na ponudbi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/different_addresses.rst:64
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Invoice Address` and :guilabel:`Delivery Address` can also be "
"edited directly from the quotation by mousing over the address and clicking "
"the :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Internal Link)` icon."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Naslov za račun` in :guilabel:`Naslov za dostavo` lahko uredite "
"tudi neposredno v ponudbi tako, da z miško premaknete kazalec nad naslov in "
"kliknete ikono :icon:`oi-arrow-right` :guilabel:`(Interna povezava)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo *Sales* application provides customers with the ability to confirm "
"orders, via an online payment, directly on a sales order. Once the sales "
"order is electronically paid for by the customer, the salesperson attached "
"to the sales order is instantly notified that the order is confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo *Sales* strankam omogoča potrditev naročil s spletnim "
"plačilom neposredno na prodajnem nalogu. Ko stranka prodajni nalog "
"elektronsko plača, je prodajalec, dodeljen prodajnemu nalogu, takoj "
"obveščen, da je naročilo potrjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:10
msgid "Activate online payments"
msgstr "Aktivirajte spletna plačila"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:12
msgid ""
"In order to have customers confirm orders with an online payment, the "
"*Online Payment* setting **must** be activated."
msgstr ""
"Da bi stranke potrdile naročila s spletnim plačilom, **mora** biti "
"nastavitev *Spletno plačilo* aktivirana."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:15
msgid ""
"To activate the *Online Payment* feature, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --"
"> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& "
"Orders` heading, check the box next to the :guilabel:`Online Payment` "
"feature, and click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za aktivacijo funkcije *Spletno plačilo* pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, pomaknite se do "
"naslova :guilabel:`Ponudbe in naročila`, označite polje poleg funkcije "
":guilabel:`Spletno plačilo` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The online payment setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Nastavitev spletnega plačila v aplikaciji Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:23
msgid ""
"Beneath the :guilabel:`Online Payment` option on the "
"*Sales* :guilabel:`Settings` page, there's a :guilabel:`Default Quotation "
"Validity` field. In this field, there's the option to add a specific number "
"of days for quotations to remain valid by default."
msgstr ""
"Pod možnostjo :guilabel:`Spletno plačilo` na strani :guilabel:`Nastavitve` "
"aplikacije *Prodaja* je polje :guilabel:`Privzeta veljavnost ponudbe`. V tem "
"polju je mogoče dodati določeno število dni, koliko časa bodo ponudbe "
"privzeto veljavne."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:27
msgid ""
"To enable this feature on a standard quotation, click the checkbox for "
"the :guilabel:`Payment` feature option, located in the :guilabel:`Online "
"confirmation` field, on the :guilabel:`Other Info` tab."
msgstr ""
"Za omogočanje te funkcije na standardni ponudbi označite polje za možnost "
"funkcije :guilabel:`Plačilo`, ki se nahaja v polju :guilabel:`Spletna "
"potrditev`, na zavihku :guilabel:`Druge informacije`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The online payment setting on a standard quotation in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Nastavitev spletnega plačila na standardni ponudbi v Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:35
msgid ""
"To enable this feature on a quotation template, click the checkbox for "
"the :guilabel:`Payment` feature option, located in the :guilabel:`Online "
"confirmation` field of the quotation template form."
msgstr ""
"Za omogočanje te funkcije na predlogi ponudbe označite polje za možnost "
"funkcije :guilabel:`Plačilo`, ki se nahaja v polju :guilabel:`Spletna "
"potrditev` obrazca predloge ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The online payment setting on quotation template forms in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Nastavitev spletnega plačila na obrazcih predlog ponudb v Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:43
msgid "Payment providers"
msgstr "Ponudniki plačilnih storitev"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:45
msgid ""
"After activating the :guilabel:`Online Payment` feature, a link to "
"configure :guilabel:`Payment Providers` appears beneath it."
msgstr ""
"Po aktivaciji funkcije :guilabel:`Spletno plačilo` se pod njo prikaže "
"povezava za konfiguracijo :guilabel:`Ponudnikov plačilnih storitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:48
msgid ""
"Clicking that link reveals a separate :guilabel:`Payment Providers` page, in "
"which a large variety of payment providers can be enabled, customized, and "
"published."
msgstr ""
"Klik na to povezavo prikaže ločeno stran :guilabel:`Ponudniki plačilnih "
"storitev`, na kateri je mogoče omogočiti, prilagoditi in objaviti veliko "
"različnih ponudnikov plačilnih storitev."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "Payment providers page in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Stran ponudnikov plačilnih storitev v Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:56
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:91
msgid ":doc:`../../../finance/payment_providers`"
msgstr ":doc:`../../../finance/payment_providers`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:59
msgid "Register a payment"
msgstr "Zabeleži plačilo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:61
msgid ""
"After opening quotations in their customer portal, customers can "
"click :guilabel:`Accept \\& Pay` to confirm their order with an online "
"payment."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranke odprejo ponudbe v svojem portalu za stranke, lahko kliknejo "
":guilabel:`Sprejmi in plačaj`, da potrdijo svoje naročilo s spletnim "
"plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The accept and pay button on an online quotation in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Gumb za sprejem in plačilo na spletni ponudbi v Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:68
msgid ""
"After clicking :guilabel:`Accept \\& Pay`, customers are presented "
"with :guilabel:`Validate Order` pop-up window containing different options "
"for them to make online payments, in the :guilabel:`Pay with` section."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na :guilabel:`Sprejmi in plačaj` se strankam prikaže pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Potrdi naročilo`, ki vsebuje različne možnosti za izvedbo "
"spletnih plačil v razdelku :guilabel:`Plačaj z`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid ""
"How to register a payment on a validate order pop-up window in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Kako registrirati plačilo v pojavnem oknu za potrditev naročila v Odoo "
"Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:77
msgid ""
"Odoo will **only** offer payment options on the :guilabel:`Validate Order` "
"pop-up window that have been published and configured on "
"the :guilabel:`Payment Providers` page."
msgstr ""
"Odoo bo na pojavnem oknu :guilabel:`Potrdi naročilo` ponudil **samo** "
"plačilne možnosti, ki so bile objavljene in konfigurirane na strani "
":guilabel:`Ponudniki plačilnih storitev`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:80
msgid ""
"Once the customer selects their desired method of payment, they will click "
"the :guilabel:`Pay` button on the pop-up window to confirm the order. Odoo "
"instantly notifies the assigned salesperson upon order confirmation with an "
"online payment."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranka izbere želeni način plačila, bo kliknila gumb :guilabel:`Plačaj` "
"v pojavnem oknu za potrditev naročila. Odoo takoj obvesti dodeljenega "
"prodajalca o potrditvi naročila s spletnim plačilom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_paid_to_validate.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sample of notification that appears in the chatter when an online payment is "
"made."
msgstr ""
"Vzorec obvestila, ki se prikaže v pogovoru, ko je izvedeno spletno plačilo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Sales** application provides customers with the ability to "
"confirm orders, via an online signature, directly on the sales order. Once "
"the sales order is electronically signed by the customer, the salesperson "
"attached to the sales order is instantly notified that the order is "
"confirmed."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija **Prodaja** v Odooju strankam omogoča potrditev naročil z "
"elektronskim podpisom neposredno na prodajnem nalogu. Ko stranke elektronsko "
"podpišejo prodajni nalog, je prodajalec, dodeljen prodajnemu nalogu, takoj "
"obveščen, da je naročilo potrjeno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:11
msgid "Activate online signatures"
msgstr "Aktiviranje spletnih podpisov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:13
msgid ""
"In order to have customers confirm orders with an online signature, the "
"*Online Signature* feature **must** be activated."
msgstr ""
"Da bi stranke potrjevale naročila s spletnim podpisom, **mora** biti "
"funkcija *Spletni podpis* aktivirana."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:16
msgid ""
"To activate the *Online Signature* feature, go to :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Configuration --> Settings`, scroll to the :guilabel:`Quotations \\& "
"Orders` heading, and activate the :guilabel:`Online Signature` feature by "
"checking the box beside it."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati funkcijo *Spletni podpis*, pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`, se "
"pomaknite do naslova :guilabel:`Ponudbe in naročila` in aktivirajte funkcijo "
":guilabel:`Spletni podpis` tako, da označite polje poleg nje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Online Signature feature option in the Settings of the Odoo Sales "
"application."
msgstr "Možnost funkcije spletnega podpisa v nastavitvah aplikacije Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:23
msgid "Then, click the :guilabel:`Save` button in the top-left corner."
msgstr "Nato kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Shrani` v zgornjem levem kotu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:26
msgid ""
"When making a quotation template, the online signature feature is "
"the :guilabel:`Signature` option, located in the :guilabel:`Online "
"confirmation` field of the quotation template form."
msgstr ""
"Pri izdelavi predloge ponudbe je funkcija spletnega podpisa možnost "
":guilabel:`Podpis`, ki se nahaja v polju :guilabel:`Spletna potrditev` "
"obrazca predloge ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:0
msgid ""
"The Online confirmation signature option found on every quotation template "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Možnost podpisa za spletno potrditev, ki jo najdete v vsaki predlogi ponudbe "
"v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:32
msgid ""
"On standard quotations, the online signature feature is "
"the :guilabel:`Signature` option, located under the :guilabel:`Other Info` "
"tab of the quotation form."
msgstr ""
"Pri standardnih ponudbah je funkcija spletnega podpisa možnost "
":guilabel:`Podpis`, ki se nahaja pod zavihkom :guilabel:`Druge informacije` "
"obrazca ponudbe."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:0
msgid ""
"The online signature feature option in the Other Info tab of a quotation "
"form in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Možnost funkcije spletnega podpisa v zavihku Druge informacije obrazca "
"ponudbe v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:39
msgid "Order confirmations with online signatures"
msgstr "Potrditve naročil s spletnimi podpisi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:41
msgid ""
"When clients access quotations online through their customer portal, there's "
"a :guilabel:`Sign \\& Pay` button directly on the quotation."
msgstr ""
"Ko stranke dostopajo do ponudb prek svojega portala za stranke, je gumb "
":guilabel:`Podpiši in plačaj` neposredno na ponudbi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The Sign and Pay button present on online quotations in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Gumb Podpiši in plačaj, ki je prisoten na spletnih ponudbah v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:47
msgid ""
"When clicked, a :guilabel:`Validate Order` pop-up window appears. In this "
"pop-up window, the :guilabel:`Full Name` field is auto-populated, based on "
"the contact information in the database."
msgstr ""
"Ko ga kliknete, se prikaže pojavno okno :guilabel:`Potrdi naročilo`. V tem "
"pojavnem oknu je polje :guilabel:`Polno ime` samodejno izpolnjeno na podlagi "
"kontaktnih podatkov v bazi podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The Validate Order pop-up window for online signatures in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Pojavno okno Potrdi naročilo za spletne podpise v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:53
msgid ""
"Then, customers have the option to enter an online signature with any of the "
"following options: :guilabel:`Auto`, :guilabel:`Draw`, or :guilabel:`Load`."
msgstr ""
"Nato imajo stranke možnost vnesti spletni podpis z eno od naslednjih "
"možnosti: :guilabel:`Samodejno`, :guilabel:`Nariši` ali :guilabel:`Naloži`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:56
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Auto` lets Odoo automatically generate an online signature based "
"on the information in the :guilabel:`Full Name` field. :guilabel:`Draw` lets "
"the customer use the cursor to create a custom signature directly on the pop-"
"up window. And :guilabel:`Load` lets the customer upload a previously-"
"created signature file from their computer."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Samodejno` omogoča, da Odoo samodejno ustvari spletni podpis na "
"podlagi informacij v polju :guilabel:`Polno ime`. :guilabel:`Nariši` omogoča "
"stranki, da uporabi kazalec za ustvarjanje podpisa po meri neposredno v "
"pojavnem oknu. :guilabel:`Naloži` pa omogoča stranki, da naloži predhodno "
"ustvarjeno datoteko s podpisom iz svojega računalnika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:61
msgid ""
"After the customer has chosen any of the three previously mentioned "
"signature options (:guilabel:`Auto`, :guilabel:`Draw`, or :guilabel:`Load`), "
"they will click the :guilabel:`Accept \\& Sign` button."
msgstr ""
"Potem ko stranka izbere eno od treh predhodno omenjenih možnosti podpisa "
"(:guilabel:`Samodejno`, :guilabel:`Nariši` ali :guilabel:`Naloži`), bo "
"kliknila gumb :guilabel:`Sprejmi in podpiši`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:65
msgid ""
"When :guilabel:`Accept \\& Sign` is clicked, the various payment method "
"options become available for them to choose from (if the *online payment* "
"option applies to this quotation)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je kliknjen gumb :guilabel:`Sprejmi in podpiši`, postanejo na voljo "
"različne možnosti načinov plačila, izmed katerih lahko izberejo (če se "
"možnost *spletno plačilo* nanaša na to ponudbo)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:68
msgid ""
"Then, when the quotation is paid and confirmed, a delivery order is "
"automatically created (if the Odoo **Inventory** app is installed)."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ponudba plačana in potrjena, se samodejno ustvari nalog za dobavo (če "
"je nameščena aplikacija **Zaloga** v Odooju)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:72
msgid "View online signatures in Developer Mode"
msgstr "Ogled elektronskih podpisov v razvijalskem načinu"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:74
msgid ""
"Clients can view the online signature in :ref:`developer mode <developer-"
"mode>`."
msgstr ""
"Stranke lahko vidijo elektronski podpis v :ref:`razvijalskem načinu "
"<developer-mode>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:76
msgid ""
"To view a online signature from a paid invoice, go to :menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Orders --> Orders` and select the desired sales order. A new "
"tab, :guilabel:`Customer Signature`, is available. Click the tab to view the "
"electronic signature as well as the :guilabel:`Signed By` "
"and :guilabel:`Signed On` information."
msgstr ""
"Če želite videti elektronski podpis iz plačanega računa, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Naročila --> Naročila` in izberite "
"želeni prodajni nalog. Na voljo je nov zavihek :guilabel:`Podpis stranke`. "
"Kliknite zavihek, da vidite elektronski podpis ter informacije "
":guilabel:`Podpisal` in :guilabel:`Podpisano dne`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/get_signature_to_validate.rst:None
msgid "The Customer Signature tab on a sales order when in Developer Mode."
msgstr "Zavihek Podpis stranke na prodajnem nalogu v razvijalskem načinu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:3
msgid "Margins"
msgstr "Marže"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:5
msgid ""
"The sales margin is the profit gained from the sale of a product or service "
"after all the costs related to it have been accounted for."
msgstr ""
"Prodajna marža je dobiček, pridobljen s prodajo izdelka ali storitve, po "
"upoštevanju vseh z njo povezanih stroškov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:8
msgid ""
"In the Odoo **Sales** application, it is possible to show sales margins on "
"quotations and sales orders. Salespeople can use the feature for better "
"management and monitoring of profitability."
msgstr ""
"V aplikaciji Odoo **Prodaja** je mogoče prikazati prodajne marže na ponudbah "
"in prodajnih nalogih. Prodajno osebje lahko uporabi to funkcijo za boljše "
"upravljanje in spremljanje donosnosti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:14
msgid ""
"To activate the *Margins* feature, go to the :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Settings`. In the :guilabel:`Pricing` section, tick "
"the :guilabel:`Margins` checkbox. Then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite aktivirati funkcijo *Marže*, pojdite v :menuselection:`aplikacija "
"Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve`. V razdelku :guilabel:`Cene` "
"označite potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Marže`. Nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:None
msgid "Margins checkbox."
msgstr "Potrditveno polje Marže."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:24
msgid "Configure price and cost"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje cene in stroškov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:26
msgid ""
"To automatically calculate the sales margin for each quotation or sales "
"order line item, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products`. "
"Fill out the :guilabel:`Sales Price` and :guilabel:`Cost` fields in "
"the :guilabel:`General Information` tab for every product."
msgstr ""
"Za samodejni izračun prodajne marže za vsako postavko ponudbe ali prodajnega "
"naloga pojdite v :menuselection:`aplikacija Prodaja --> Izdelki --> "
"Izdelki`. Izpolnite polji :guilabel:`Prodajna cena` in :guilabel:`Stroški` v "
"zavihku :guilabel:`Splošne informacije` za vsak izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:30
msgid "Odoo calculates the margin by:"
msgstr "Odoo izračuna maržo kot:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:32
msgid ""
"Sales~Margin = Sales~Price - Cost\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"Prodajna~marža = Prodajna~cena - Stroški\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:35
msgid "The margin percentage is calculated by:"
msgstr "Odstotek marže se izračuna kot:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:37
msgid ""
"\\frac{Sales~Price - Cost~Price}{Sales~Price} \\times 100\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\frac{Prodajna~cena - Nabavna~cena}{Prodajna~cena} \\times 100\n"
"\n"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:None
msgid "Cable Management box product page."
msgstr "Stran izdelka škatla za upravljanje kablov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:44
msgid "Compute margins on sales orders"
msgstr "Izračun marž na prodajnih nalogih"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:46
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations` and click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button to begin a new quotation. Fill out the quotation "
"with the necessary information. While adding products to the quotation, a "
"new field, :guilabel:`Margin`, automatically appears at the bottom of the "
"document. This field displays the order's total margin in the configured "
"currency as well as the percentage."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite v :menuselection:`aplikacija Prodaja --> Naročila --> Ponudbe` in "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo`, da začnete novo ponudbo. Izpolnite ponudbo z "
"zahtevanimi informacijami. Med dodajanjem izdelkov k ponudbi se na dnu "
"dokumenta samodejno prikaže novo polje :guilabel:`Marža`. To polje prikazuje "
"skupno maržo naročila v konfigurirani valuti ter odstotek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:None
msgid "Sales order with Margin field on the bottom."
msgstr "Prodajni nalog s poljem Marža na dnu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:55
msgid ""
"To display a product's margin and the margin percentage per line item, click "
"the :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(settings adjust)` icon in "
"the :guilabel:`Order Lines` tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite prikazati maržo izdelka in odstotek marže za posamezno postavko, "
"kliknite ikono :icon:`oi-settings-adjust` :guilabel:`(prilagajanje "
"nastavitev)` v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:58
msgid ""
"Then, tick the checkboxes for :guilabel:`Margin` and :guilabel:`Margin(%)`. "
"The :guilabel:`Margin` column shows the profit to earn from the sale after "
"accounting for all associated costs. It displays in the configured currency "
"value. The :guilabel:`Margin(%)` shows the margin value as a percentage. The "
"margin for one unit is multiplied by the quantity to determine the margin "
"for the entire line."
msgstr ""
"Nato označite potrditveni polji za :guilabel:`Marža` in :guilabel:`Marža (%)"
"`. Stolpec :guilabel:`Marža` prikazuje dobiček, ki ga je mogoče pridobiti s "
"prodajo po upoštevanju vseh povezanih stroškov. Prikaže se v konfigurirani "
"valutni vrednosti. Stolpec :guilabel:`Marža (%)` prikazuje vrednost marže "
"kot odstotek. Marža za eno enoto se pomnoži s količino, da se določi marža "
"za celotno vrstico."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:63
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Margin` and :guilabel:`Margin(%)` columns are not displayed "
"by default, but once enabled, the columns appear on all new and existing "
"quotations and :abbr:`SOs (sales orders)`."
msgstr ""
"Stolpca :guilabel:`Marža` in :guilabel:`Marža (%)` nista privzeto prikazana, "
"vendar se po omogočitvi prikažeta na vseh novih in obstoječih ponudbah ter "
":abbr:`PN (prodajnih nalogih)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:None
msgid "Sales order with Margin and Margin(%) columns displayed."
msgstr "Prodajni nalog s prikazanima stolpcema Marža in Marža (%)."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:70
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Margin` and :guilabel:`Margin (%)` columns are not editable "
"since they are automatic calculations. To change the calculation, refer "
"to :ref:`Configure price and cost <sales_quotations/margin/configure-price-"
"and-cost>` section for more information."
msgstr ""
"Stolpca :guilabel:`Marža` in :guilabel:`Marža (%)` nista uredljiva, saj gre "
"za samodejne izračune. Če želite spremeniti izračun, glejte razdelek "
":ref:`Konfiguriranje cene in stroškov <sales_quotations/margin/configure-"
"price-and-cost>` za več informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:75
msgid "Margin calculation with a pricelist"
msgstr "Izračun marže s cenikom"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:77
msgid ""
"To calculate the margin with an applied pricelist, begin with configuring a "
"pricelist for the product. Follow these steps:"
msgstr ""
"Za izračun marže s prijavljenim cenikom začnite s konfiguracijo cenika za "
"izdelek. Sledite tem korakom:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:80
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Pricelists` and click "
"the :guilabel:`New` button."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Izdelki --> Ceniki` in "
"kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Novo`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:82
msgid ""
"Enter the name of the pricelist and click :guilabel:`Add a line` to create a "
"new pricelist rule."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ime cenika in kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj vrstico`, da ustvarite novo "
"pravilo cenika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:84
msgid "Configure the pricelist and click :guilabel:`Save & Close` button."
msgstr "Konfigurirajte cenik in kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Shrani in zapri`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:85
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations` and create a "
"quotation."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Sales --> Naročila --> Ponudbe` in "
"ustvarite ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:86
msgid "In the :guilabel:`Pricelist` field, select the newly made pricelist."
msgstr "V polju :guilabel:`Cenik` izberite novo ustvarjen cenik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:87
msgid ""
"Click on :guilabel:`Update Prices` to refresh the product price and margin."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na :guilabel:`Posodobi cene`, da osvežite ceno in maržo izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:90
msgid ""
"To apply a seasonal 5% discount on blue denim jeans that requires a minumim "
"of two pairs of jeans in an order and is valid only from October to the end "
"of December, the pricelist rule should look like this:"
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo sezonskega 5% popusta na modre kavbojke, ki zahteva najmanj dva "
"para kavbojk v naročilu in velja samo od oktobra do konca decembra, bi "
"moralo pravilo cenika izgledati takole:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:0
msgid "Pricelist Rules pop-up window."
msgstr "Pojavno okno pravil cenika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:97
msgid ""
"After saving the pricelist, go to the desired :abbr:`SO (sales order)` and "
"select the newly created pricelist, and adjust the quantity according to the "
"pricelist's rule."
msgstr ""
"Po shranjevanju cenika pojdite na želeni :abbr:`PN (prodajni nalog)` in "
"izberite novo ustvarjen cenik ter prilagodite količino glede na pravilo "
"cenika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:0
msgid "Sales order with a new pricelist selected."
msgstr "Prodajni nalog z izbranim novim cenikom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:103
msgid ""
"After the changes are made, click :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Update "
"Prices` to update the :guilabel:`Margin`, :guilabel:`Margin (%)`, "
"and :guilabel:`Amount`. The margin is recalculated based on the pricelist-"
"adjusted product's sales price and cost."
msgstr ""
"Ko so spremembe narejene, kliknite :icon:`fa-refresh` :guilabel:`Posodobi "
"cene`, da posodobite :guilabel:`Marža`, :guilabel:`Marža (%)` in "
":guilabel:`Znesek`. Marža se ponovno izračuna na podlagi prodajne cene in "
"stroškov izdelka, prilagojenih glede na cenik."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:0
msgid ""
"Sales order with margins recalculated based on the price-list adjustment."
msgstr ""
"Prodajni nalog z maržami, ponovno izračunanimi na podlagi prilagoditve "
"cenika."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/margin.rst:111
msgid ""
"Another way to visualize the impact of margins on sales orders is to go "
"to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Orders --> Quotations`, select "
"the :icon:`fa-area-chart` :guilabel:`(area chart)` icon or :icon:`oi-view-"
"pivot` :guilabel:`(pivot)` icon, click :guilabel:`Measures` button and "
"change it to :guilabel:`Margin` to see margin contributions across the "
"customer base."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:5
msgid ""
"The use of optional products is a marketing strategy that involves the cross-"
"selling of useful and related products alongside a desired core product. For "
"instance, when a business configures optional products in their Odoo "
"database, an eCommerce or Website customer could be suggested a mouse and "
"keyboard or an extended warranty when they add a laptop to their shopping "
"cart."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba izbirnih izdelkov je marketinška strategija, ki vključuje navzkrižno "
"prodajo koristnih in sorodnih izdelkov skupaj z želenim osnovnim izdelkom. "
"Na primer, ko podjetje konfigurira izbirne izdelke v svoji podatkovni bazi "
"Odoo, se lahko stranki v e-trgovini ali na spletnem mestu predlaga miška in "
"tipkovnica ali podaljšana garancija, ko doda prenosni računalnik v "
"nakupovalni voziček."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:10
msgid ""
"Optional products are automatically suggested during the quotation process "
"whenever an associated core product is added to a quote. They are also "
"suggested in e-commerce interactions when a customer adds an associated core "
"product to their shopping cart."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:15
msgid ""
"Optional products differ from :doc:`accessory and alternative products </"
"applications/websites/ecommerce/products/cross_upselling>` in terms of where "
"they are displayed during customers' online shopping journeys."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:20
msgid "Configuring optional products"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje izbirnih izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:22
msgid ""
"With the Odoo **Sales** app, it is possible to add optional products "
"directly to product forms. To add an optional product to a product form, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Sales --> Products --> Products` and choose a "
"product."
msgstr ""
"Z aplikacijo Odoo **Sales** je mogoče izbirne izdelke dodati neposredno na "
"obrazce izdelkov. Če želite izbirni izdelek dodati na obrazec izdelka, "
"pojdite na :menuselection:`Sales --> Izdelki --> Izdelki` in izberite "
"izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:26
msgid ""
"Ensure that the product's :guilabel:`Sales` checkbox is checked and click "
"the :guilabel:`Sales` tab. Under :guilabel:`Upsell & Cross-sell` heading, "
"the :guilabel:`Optional Products` drop-down menu allows for optional "
"products to be set. Products will be displayed in alphabetical order. If the "
"desired product isn't readily visible, type its name in the field to bring "
"it up, then select it to add it as an optional product."
msgstr ""
"Prepričajte se, da je potrditveno polje :guilabel:`Sales` izdelka označeno, "
"in kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Sales`. Pod naslovom :guilabel:`Upsell & "
"Cross-sell` spustni meni :guilabel:`Optional Products` omogoča nastavitev "
"izbirnih izdelkov. Izdelki bodo prikazani po abecednem vrstnem redu. Če "
"želeni izdelek ni takoj viden, vnesite njegovo ime v polje, da ga "
"prikličete, nato pa ga izberite, da ga dodate kot izbirni izdelek."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:32
msgid ""
"To delete an optional product from the product form, simply click "
"the :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(Delete)` icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izbrisati izbirni izdelek iz obrazca izdelka, preprosto kliknite "
"ikono :icon:`fa-times` :guilabel:`(Izbriši)`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:None
msgid ""
"Where the optional products section appears in product forms in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""
"Kje se oddelek izbirnih izdelkov pojavi v obrazcih izdelkov v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:38
msgid ""
"Additional products can also be added to a core product by "
"clicking :guilabel:`Search more...`. This opens the :guilabel:`Search: "
"Optional Products` form, which displays all products in the catalog and "
"includes the :guilabel:`New` button to create a new product. Multiple "
"products may be selected as optional products at once when using this form "
"by clicking their checkboxes and then clicking :guilabel:`Select`."
msgstr ""
"Dodatne izdelke lahko osnovnemu izdelku dodate tudi s klikom na "
":guilabel:`Iskanje več...`. To odpre obrazec :guilabel:`Iskanje: Izbirni "
"izdelki`, ki prikazuje vse izdelke v katalogu in vključuje gumb "
":guilabel:`Novo` za ustvarjanje novega izdelka. Pri uporabi tega obrazca "
"lahko hkrati izberete več izdelkov kot izbirne izdelke s klikom na njihova "
"potrditvena polja in nato s klikom na :guilabel:`Izberi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:None
msgid "The Search: Optional Products form accessed by clicking Search more..."
msgstr ""
"Obrazec Iskanje: Izbirni izdelki, do katerega dostopate s klikom na Iskanje "
"več..."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:48
msgid "Optional products on quotation templates and quotations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:50
msgid ""
"Optional products can be added to quotation templates, allowing sales staff "
"to offer related products without needing to manually add them to each "
"quote. Additional optional products can also be added to individual "
"quotations when needed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:55
msgid "Quotations"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:57
msgid ""
"To add additional products on an individual quote, navigate "
"to :menuselection:`Sales --> Orders --> Quotations` and select an existing "
"quote or :doc:`create a new quote <create_quotations>`. Then open "
"the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab. Doing so reveals a blank field in "
"the :guilabel:`Product` column. Click :guilabel:`Add a product`. When "
"clicked, a drop-down menu with products from the database appear. Select the "
"desired product from the drop-down menu to add it as an optional product. "
"Type the name of the desired product or click :guilabel:`Search More...` to "
"find additional products."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:65
msgid ""
"To delete any line item from the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab, click "
"the :icon:`fa-trash-o` :guilabel:`(delete)` icon."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:69
msgid ""
"When a product is added, the default :guilabel:`Quantity` is `1`, but can be "
"updated."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:74
msgid ""
"Quotation templates also have an *Optional Products* tab, where related "
"products or services can be added. To add optional products to a quotation "
"template, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> "
"Quotation Templates`. Then, either select an existing quotation template to "
"edit or :doc:`create a new one <quote_template>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:79
msgid ""
"On the quotation template form, click the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab. "
"Then, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the desired product to add as "
"an optional product to the quotation template."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:83
msgid ""
"When the configured quotation template is used, the products added in "
"the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab will appear in the corresponding tab "
"in the quotation. These products can be removed and additional products can "
"be added before the quotation is sent to a customer."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:None
msgid "The Optional Products section in a quotation template in Odoo Sales."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:91
msgid ""
"There is no limit to how many optional products can be added to a quotation "
"template."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:94
msgid "Previewing optional products"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:96
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Preview` button, located in the upper-left corner of "
"the quotation, to reveal a preview of the quotation email customers would "
"receive. Optional products are located in the :guilabel:`Options` section of "
"the preview."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:100
msgid ""
"Customers are able to add different optional products to an order by "
"clicking the :icon:`fa-shopping-cart` :guilabel:`(Add to cart)` icon, "
"located to the right of the optional product line."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:None
msgid "The Options section within a quotation preview."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:107
msgid ""
"If a customer selects optional products, they are automatically added to the "
"quotation managed by the salesperson."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/optional_products.rst:110
msgid ""
"When a customer adds optional products to an order, the salesperson is "
"instantly notified about the change, along with any other change the "
"customer makes to an order. This allows salespeople to stay up-to-date with "
"everything related to an order in the backend of the *Sales* application. "
"Added products appear in green in the :guilabel:`Optional Products` tab when "
"the quote is viewed."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:5
msgid ""
"Before getting into detail about how to use product variants on quotations "
"and sales orders, it's recommended to learn about :doc:`../products_prices/"
"products/variants` in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Preden se podrobneje seznanite s tem, kako uporabljati različice izdelkov na "
"ponudbah in prodajnih nalogih, je priporočljivo, da se seznanite z :doc:`../"
"products_prices/products/variants` v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:8
msgid ""
"Once familiarized with the basics surrounding product variants, the "
"following covers how product variants can be added to quotations and sales "
"orders using the *product configurator* or *order grid entry*."
msgstr ""
"Ko se seznanite z osnovami glede različic izdelkov, v nadaljevanju "
"opisujemo, kako lahko različice izdelkov dodate na ponudbe in prodajne "
"naloge z uporabo *konfiguratorja izdelkov* ali *vnosa v mrežo naročil*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:13
msgid ""
"It should be noted that the setting is titled, *Variant Grid Entry* on the "
"*Sales* app settings page, and titled, *Order Grid Entry* on product forms. "
"So, be sure to keep that in mind."
msgstr ""
"Opozoriti je treba, da je nastavitev naslovljena *Vnos v mrežo različic* na "
"strani z nastavitvami aplikacije *Prodaja* in naslovljena *Vnos v mrežo "
"naročil* na obrazcih izdelkov. To imejte v mislih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:19
msgid ""
"When working with product variants, Odoo uses the product configurator, by "
"default. To add the variant grid entry option, that feature **must** be "
"enabled in the Odoo *Sales* application. The variant grid entry option "
"provides a pop-up window on the quotation/sales order to simplify the "
"variant selection process."
msgstr ""
"Pri delu z različicami izdelkov Odoo privzeto uporablja konfigurator "
"izdelkov. Za dodajanje možnosti vnosa v mrežo različic **mora** biti ta "
"funkcija omogočena v aplikaciji Odoo *Prodaja*. Možnost vnosa v mrežo "
"različic ponuja pojavno okno na ponudbi/prodajnem nalogu za poenostavitev "
"postopka izbire različic."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:24
msgid ""
"To enable that setting, go to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --"
"> Settings`, and scroll to the :guilabel:`Product Catalog` section. Then, "
"check the box next to the :guilabel:`Variant Grid Entry` option, and "
"click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Za omogočanje te nastavitve pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija "
"Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Nastavitve` in se pomaknite do razdelka "
":guilabel:`Katalog izdelkov`. Nato potrdite polje poleg možnosti "
":guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo različic` in kliknite :guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:None
msgid "The variant grid entry setting in the Odoo Sales application."
msgstr "Nastavitev vnosa v mrežo različic v aplikaciji Odoo Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:33
msgid ""
"Of course, the :guilabel:`Variants` feature **must** also be activated, in "
"order to use product variants on quotations and sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Seveda mora biti omogočena tudi funkcija :guilabel:`Različice`, da lahko "
"uporabljate različice izdelkov na ponudbah in prodajnih nalogih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:39
msgid ""
"Once the :guilabel:`Variant Grid Entry` setting is enabled, both options "
"(*Product Configurator* and *Order Grid Entry*) become available on every "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Ko je nastavitev :guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo različic` omogočena, postaneta obe "
"možnosti (*Konfigurator izdelkov* in *Vnos v mrežo naročil*) na voljo na "
"vsakem obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:42
msgid ""
"To configure a product form to use either a product configurator or variant "
"grid entry, start by navigating to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --"
"> Products` to view all the products in the database."
msgstr ""
"Za konfiguracijo obrazca izdelka za uporabo konfiguratorja izdelkov ali "
"vnosa v mrežo različic začnite tako, da se pomaknete na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki`, da si ogledate "
"vse izdelke v zbirki podatkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:46
msgid ""
"Then, select the desired product to configure, or click :guilabel:`New`, to "
"create a new product from scratch. Once on the product form, click into "
"the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab, where product variants can be "
"viewed, modified, and added."
msgstr ""
"Nato izberite želeni izdelek za konfiguracijo ali kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, "
"da ustvarite nov izdelek od začetka. Ko ste na obrazcu izdelka, kliknite v "
"zavihek :guilabel:`Atributi in različice`, kjer si lahko ogledate, "
"spremenite in dodate različice izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:50
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the :guilabel:`Attributes \\& Variants` tab, there is "
"a :guilabel:`Sales Variant Selection` section with two "
"options: :guilabel:`Product Configurator` and :guilabel:`Order Grid Entry`."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu zavihka :guilabel:`Atributi in različice` je razdelek "
":guilabel:`Izbira različic pri prodaji` z dvema možnostma: "
":guilabel:`Konfigurator izdelkov` in :guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo naročil`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:55
msgid ""
"It should be noted that these options **only** appear if at least two values "
"of an attribute have been added to the record."
msgstr ""
"Opozoriti je treba, da se te možnosti pokažejo **samo**, če sta bila zapisu "
"dodani vsaj dve vrednosti atributa."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"Sales variant selection options on the attributes and variants tab on "
"product form."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti izbire različic pri prodaji na zavihku atributi in različice na "
"obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:62
msgid ""
"These options determine which method is used when adding product variants to "
"quotations or sales orders."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti določajo, katera metoda se uporabi pri dodajanju različic "
"izdelkov na ponudbe ali prodajne naloge."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:65
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Configurator` provides a pop-up window that neatly "
"displays all the available product variants for that particular product when "
"it's added to a quotation. However, only one variant can be selected/added "
"at a time."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konfigurator izdelkov` ponuja pojavno okno, ki pregledno prikaže "
"vse razpoložljive različice izdelkov za določen izdelek, ko je dodan na "
"ponudbo. Vendar je mogoče izbrati/dodati samo eno različico naenkrat."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:69
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Order Grid Entry` provides the same information as "
"the :guilabel:`Product Configurator` in a table layout, allowing the user to "
"select larger numbers of unique product variants, and add them to a "
"quotation/sales order, in a single view."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo naročil` ponuja enake informacije kot "
":guilabel:`Konfigurator izdelkov` v razpredelnici, kar uporabniku omogoča "
"izbiro večjega števila edinstvenih različic izdelkov in njihov dodatek na "
"ponudbo/prodajni nalog v enem pogledu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:74
msgid "Product configurator"
msgstr "Konfigurator izdelkov"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:76
msgid ""
"The product configurator feature appears as a :guilabel:`Configure` pop-up "
"window, as soon as a product with (at least two) variants is added to a "
"quotation or sales order, but **only** if the :guilabel:`Product "
"Configurator` option is selected on its product form."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija konfiguratorja izdelkov se prikaže kot pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Konfiguriraj`, takoj ko je izdelek z (vsaj dvema) različicama "
"dodan na ponudbo ali prodajni nalog, vendar **samo**, če je na njegovem "
"obrazcu izdelka izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Konfigurator izdelkov`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The product configurator pop-up window that appears on a quotation or sales "
"order."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno konfiguratorja izdelka, ki se prikaže na ponudbi ali prodajnem "
"nalogu."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:85
msgid ""
"This :guilabel:`Configure` pop-up window also appears if "
"the :guilabel:`Order Grid Entry` setting is **not** activated, as it is the "
"default option Odoo uses when dealing with product variants on quotations "
"and/or sales orders."
msgstr ""
"To pojavno okno :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj` se prikaže tudi, če nastavitev "
":guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo naročila` **ni** aktivirana, saj je to privzeta "
"možnost, ki jo Odoo uporablja pri delu z različicami izdelkov na ponudbah in/"
"ali prodajnih nalogih."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:89
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Product Configurator` option lets salespeople choose exactly "
"which product variant to add to the quotation or sales order using a format "
"similar to online shopping."
msgstr ""
"Možnost :guilabel:`Konfigurator izdelka` prodajalcem omogoča, da izberejo "
"točno določeno različico izdelka, ki jo želijo dodati na ponudbo ali "
"prodajni nalog, v obliki, podobni spletni trgovini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:93
msgid "Order grid entry"
msgstr "Vnos v mrežo naročila"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:95
msgid ""
"The order grid entry feature appears as a :guilabel:`Choose Product "
"Variants` pop-up window, as soon as a product with (at least two) variants "
"is added to a quotation or sales order, but **only** if the :guilabel:`Order "
"Grid Entry` option is selected on its product form."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija vnosa v mrežo naročila se prikaže kot pojavno okno "
":guilabel:`Izberi različice izdelka`, takoj ko je izdelek z (vsaj dvema) "
"različicama dodan na ponudbo ali prodajni nalog, vendar **le**, če je "
"možnost :guilabel:`Vnos v mrežo naročila` izbrana na obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"The choose product variants pop-up window that appears on a quotation in "
"Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno za izbiro različic izdelka, ki se prikaže na ponudbi v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:103
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Choose Product Variants` pop-up window features all the "
"variant options for that particular product. From this pop-up window, the "
"salesperson can designate how many of each variant they'd like to add to the "
"quotation/sales order at once."
msgstr ""
"Pojavno okno :guilabel:`Izberi različice izdelka` prikazuje vse možnosti "
"različic za ta določen izdelek. V tem pojavnem oknu lahko prodajalec določi, "
"koliko kosov posamezne različice želi naenkrat dodati na ponudbo/prodajni "
"nalog."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:107
msgid ""
"When all the desired quantities and variants have been selected, the "
"salesperson simply clicks :guilabel:`Confirm`, and those orders are "
"instantly added to the quotation/sales order in the :guilabel:`Order Lines` "
"tab."
msgstr ""
"Ko so izbrane vse želene količine in različice, prodajalec preprosto klikne "
":guilabel:`Potrdi` in ta naročila so takoj dodana na ponudbo/prodajni nalog "
"v zavihku :guilabel:`Vrstice naročila`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:None
msgid ""
"Populated order lines tab after order grid entry has been chosen to select "
"products."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek z vrsticami naročila po tem, ko je bil uporabljen vnos v mrežo "
"naročila za izbiro izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/orders_and_variants.rst:116
msgid ":doc:`../products_prices/products/variants`"
msgstr ":doc:`../products_prices/products/variants`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:8
msgid ""
"The *PDF Quote Builder* in the Odoo **Sales** app transforms a standard, "
"text-heavy quote into a polished, branded proposal. Instead of sending a "
"table of products and prices, it enables users to sandwich a quotation "
"between professionally designed PDF pages."
msgstr ""
"*Graditelj ponudb v PDF* v aplikaciji Odoo **Sales** pretvori standardno "
"ponudbo, ki je bogata z besedilom, v uglajeno, blagovno zavarovano predlog. "
"Namesto pošiljanja tabele izdelkov in cen omogoča uporabnikom, da ponudbo "
"vstavijo med profesionalno oblikovane PDF strani."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:12
msgid ""
"The PDF Quote Builder seamlessly combines user-provided marketing documents, "
"technical sheets, branded cover pages, and Odoo-generated quotes in one "
"document. Quotation templates can be configured to include specific PDFs in "
"the quote, ensuring documents reach the intended customers. Dynamic text in "
"PDF templates allows users to extract **Sales** app data and customize files "
"for each project or customer."
msgstr ""
"Graditelj ponudb v PDF brezhibno združuje uporabniško zagotovljene "
"marketinške dokumente, tehnične liste, blagovne naslovne strani in ponudbe, "
"ki jih ustvari Odoo, v enem dokumentu. Predloge ponudb je mogoče "
"konfigurirati tako, da vključujejo določene PDF-je v ponudbi, s čimer "
"zagotavljajo, da dokumenti dosežejo ciljne stranke. Dinamično besedilo v PDF "
"predlogah omogoča uporabnikom pridobivanje podatkov iz aplikacije **Sales** "
"in prilagajanje datotek za vsak projekt ali stranko."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:18
msgid ""
"Empty text fields on the PDF can be completed directly from the quotation "
"form in the **Sales** app. This approach lets users personalize quotes "
"without editing the PDF itself."
msgstr ""
"Prazna besedilna polja v PDF-ju je mogoče izpolniti neposredno iz obrazca "
"ponudbe v aplikaciji **Sales**. Ta pristop uporabnikom omogoča prilagajanje "
"ponudb brez urejanja samega PDF-ja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:21
msgid ""
"Users can also configure PDFs on the product form. These files are then "
"automatically added to the quote when a product is included. Beyond "
"assembling quotes, the PDF Quote Builder also enables PDFs to be featured on "
"the online store product page. This ensures customers can access detailed "
"product information directly on the website."
msgstr ""
"Uporabniki lahko konfigurirajo tudi PDF-je na obrazcu izdelka. Te datoteke "
"se nato samodejno dodajo ponudbi, ko je izdelek vključen. Poleg sestavljanja "
"ponudb Graditelj ponudb v PDF omogoča tudi prikazovanje PDF-jev na strani "
"izdelka v spletni trgovini. To zagotavlja, da stranke lahko dostopajo do "
"podrobnih informacij o izdelku neposredno na spletni strani."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:27
msgid ""
"`Odoo Quick Tips - Create a PDF quote [video] <https://www.youtube.com/watch?"
"v=tQNydBZt-VI>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Odoo hitri nasveti - Ustvari ponudbo PDF [video] <https://www.youtube.com/"
"watch?v=tQNydBZt-VI>`_"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:30
msgid ""
"It is recommended to edit PDF forms with Adobe software. The form fields in "
"the header and footer PDF templates are required to retrieve dynamic values "
"in Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Priporočljivo je, da PDF obrazce urejate s programsko opremo Adobe. Polja "
"obrazca v predlogah glave in noge PDF so potrebna za pridobivanje dinamičnih "
"vrednosti v Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:35
msgid "Add dynamic text to PDFs"
msgstr "Dodajte dinamično besedilo v PDF-je"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:35
msgid "Add dynamic text fields to PDFs."
msgstr "Dodajte dinamična besedilna polja v PDF-je."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:40
msgid "Add PDFs to quotes"
msgstr "Dodaj PDF-je ponudbam"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:40
msgid "Add a PDF header or footer to a quote."
msgstr "Dodaj glavo ali nogo PDF ponudbi."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:45
msgid "Add PDFs to products"
msgstr "Dodaj PDF-je izdelkom"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:45
msgid ""
"Set up the PDF headers and footers for products. These appear on sales "
"quotes and online store pages."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite glave in noge PDF za izdelke. Te se prikažejo na prodajnih "
"ponudbah in straneh spletne trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:55
msgid ""
"To add custom PDF files to quotes, the :guilabel:`PDF Quote builder` feature "
"*must* be configured."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje datotek PDF po meri v ponudbe *mora* biti konfigurirana "
"funkcija :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudb PDF`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:57
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Settings`. "
"Scroll to the *Quotations & Orders* section, enable the :guilabel:`PDF Quote "
"builder` feature, then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> "
"Nastavitve`. Pomaknite se do razdelka *Ponudbe in naročila*, omogočite "
"funkcijo :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudb PDF` in nato kliknite "
":guilabel:`Shrani`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:61
msgid "Add PDF as Header/Footer"
msgstr "Dodaj PDF kot glavo/nogo"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:64
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:44
msgid ""
"Odoo does not permit spaces in PDF field names. Only use letters, numbers, "
"hyphens, or underscores."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ne dovoljuje presledkov v imenih polj PDF. Uporabljajte samo črke, "
"številke, pomišljaje ali podčrtaje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:67
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Sales** app can add a custom PDF as a header or footer. "
"The :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab in a quote allows the selection of "
"multiple headers and footers for insertion into the final PDF quote."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo **Prodaja** lahko doda datoteko PDF po meri kot glavo ali "
"nogo. Zavihek :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudb` v ponudbi omogoča izbiro več glav "
"in nog za vstavljanje v končno ponudbo PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:71
msgid ""
"To add a custom PDF as a header or footer, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Configuration --> Headers/Footers`. On this page, "
"click :guilabel:`New` to create a new header or footer, or "
"click :guilabel:`Upload` to add a PDF file."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje datoteke PDF po meri kot glave ali noge pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Glave/Noge`. Na tej "
"strani kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da ustvarite novo glavo ali nogo, ali "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži`, da dodate datoteko PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:75
msgid ""
"Clicking :guilabel:`Upload` lets the user select a PDF file from their "
"computer. Select the :guilabel:`Document Type` to set the order in which the "
"PDF appears in the quote. :guilabel:`Header` places the PDF before the "
"quote, and :guilabel:`Footer` places it after. Further configuration can be "
"done by clicking the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` "
"icon in the top-right corner of the document card and "
"selecting :guilabel:`Edit`."
msgstr ""
"Klik na :guilabel:`Naloži` uporabniku omogoči izbiro datoteke PDF iz "
"računalnika. Izberite :guilabel:`Vrsta dokumenta`, da nastavite vrstni red, "
"v katerem se PDF prikaže v ponudbi. :guilabel:`Glava` postavi PDF pred "
"ponudbo, :guilabel:`Noga` pa ga postavi za njo. Nadaljnjo konfiguracijo "
"lahko izvedete s klikom na ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična "
"tripičje)` v zgornjem desnem kotu kartice dokumenta in izbiro "
":guilabel:`Uredi`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:81
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank document form. In the :guilabel:`File "
"Content` field, click the :guilabel:`Upload your file` button and select the "
"PDF to upload. Once uploaded, Odoo automatically names the document after "
"the file name. The :guilabel:`Name` field then becomes editable."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da odprete prazen obrazec dokumenta. V polju "
":guilabel:`Vsebina datoteke` kliknite gumb :guilabel:`Naloži datoteko` in "
"izberite datoteko PDF za nalaganje. Ko je naložena, Odoo samodejno poimenuje "
"dokument po imenu datoteke. Polje :guilabel:`Ime` nato postane uredljivo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:86
msgid ""
"To modify the uploaded file, click the :icon:`fa-"
"pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)`, :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`(Download)`, "
"or :icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Clear)` icon next to the file name. If the "
"PDF includes form fields, they are automatically recognized as dynamic text "
"fields. View and edit these fields by clicking :guilabel:`Configure dynamic "
"fields`. For more details, refer to :doc:`pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text`."
msgstr ""
"Za spremembo naložene datoteke kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`"
"(Uredi)`, :icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`(Prenesi)` ali :icon:`fa-trash` "
":guilabel:`(Počisti)` poleg imena datoteke. Če PDF vključuje polja obrazca, "
"so samodejno prepoznana kot dinamična besedilna polja. Oglejte si in uredite "
"ta polja s klikom na :guilabel:`Konfiguriraj dinamična polja`. Za več "
"podrobnosti glejte :doc:`pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:92
msgid ""
"The :doc:`quote_template` field assigns the PDF to the selected template, "
"restricting the PDF's use to that template."
msgstr ""
"Polje :doc:`quote_template` dodeli PDF izbrani predlogi in omeji uporabo "
"datoteke PDF na to predlogo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:96
msgid ""
"Headers and footers can also be added to a quotation template by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Configuration --> Quotation Templates`. "
"Select a template and then in the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` "
"tab, :guilabel:`Add` or :guilabel:`Upload` a PDF directly."
msgstr ""
"Glave in noge lahko dodate tudi predlogi ponudbe tako, da greste na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Predloge ponudb`. "
"Izberite predlogo in nato v zavihku :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudb` "
":guilabel:`Dodajte` ali :guilabel:`Naložite` datoteko PDF neposredno."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:103
msgid "A configured document form for a header."
msgstr "Konfiguriran obrazec dokumenta za glavo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder.rst:103
msgid ""
"The HVAC PDF file is configured as a Header and the **Sales** app recognizes "
"the form fields as dynamic text fields."
msgstr ""
"Datoteka HVAC PDF je konfigurirana kot glava in aplikacija **Prodaja** "
"prepozna polja obrazca kot dinamična besedilna polja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:3
msgid "Add a PDF or a URL to a product"
msgstr "Dodajte datoteko PDF ali URL izdelku"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:5
msgid ""
"The Odoo **Sales** app lets users add a custom PDF or URL to a *product "
"template* or variant using the PDF Quote builder. By attaching a PDF or a "
"URL, users can include extra information or resources in their quotes, "
"online product pages, or for manufacturing."
msgstr ""
"Aplikacija Odoo **Prodaja** uporabnikom omogoča dodajanje datoteke PDF po "
"meri ali URL-ja *predlogi izdelka* ali različici z uporabo graditelja ponudb "
"PDF. Z dodajanjem datoteke PDF ali URL-ja lahko uporabniki vključijo dodatne "
"informacije ali vire v svoje ponudbe, spletne strani izdelkov ali za "
"proizvodnjo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:12
msgid "Add a PDF or URL to a product template"
msgstr "Dodajte datoteko PDF ali URL predlogi izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:14
msgid ""
"To add a custom PDF to a product template, go to the :menuselection:`Sales "
"app --> Products --> Products`, and select the desired product. Next, click "
"the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button at the top of the product template "
"page."
msgstr ""
"Za dodajanje datoteke PDF po meri predlogi izdelka pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki` in izberite "
"želeni izdelek. Nato kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Dokumenti` na vrhu "
"strani predloge izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:None
msgid "The Documents smart button on a Sales product form."
msgstr "Pametni gumb Dokumenti na obrazcu izdelka v aplikaciji Prodaja."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:21
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`Upload` to open the user's local file directory then select "
"and upload a PDF to Odoo. Odoo automatically creates a PDF document form "
"from the uploaded PDF, with the :guilabel:`Sales Visibility` set "
"to :guilabel:`Hidden` and the :guilabel:`Publish on website` toggle disabled "
"by default. Click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(vertical ellipsis)` "
"icon in the corner of the document card and select :guilabel:`Edit` to "
"further :ref:`configure the PDF form <sales/pdf_quote_builder/"
"add_pdf_products/pdf-form-configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Naloži`, da odprete lokalni imenik datotek uporabnika, "
"nato izberite in naložite datoteko PDF v Odoo. Odoo samodejno ustvari "
"obrazec dokumenta PDF iz naložene datoteke PDF, pri čemer je "
":guilabel:`Vidnost prodaje` nastavljena na :guilabel:`Skrito` in je stikalo "
":guilabel:`Objavi na spletni strani` privzeto onemogočeno. Kliknite ikono "
":icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` :guilabel:`(navpična tripičje)` v kotu kartice "
"dokumenta in izberite :guilabel:`Uredi`, da nadalje :ref:`konfigurirate "
"obrazec PDF <sales/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products/pdf-form-configuration>"
"`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:28
msgid ""
"Click :guilabel:`New` to open a blank PDF form and manually :ref:`configure "
"the document form <sales/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products/pdf-form-"
"configuration>`."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite :guilabel:`Novo`, da odprete prazen obrazec PDF in ročno "
":ref:`konfigurirate obrazec dokumenta <sales/pdf_quote_builder/"
"add_pdf_products/pdf-form-configuration>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:35
msgid "Add a PDF or URL to a product variant"
msgstr "Dodajte datoteko PDF ali URL različici izdelka"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:37
msgid ""
"A PDF document or URL can also be added to a product variant, rather than "
"the product template. The document form for the product variant is the same "
"as the product template's document form, **except** it doesn't include the "
"*E-Commerce* section and thus cannot be published on the website."
msgstr ""
"Dokument PDF ali URL je mogoče dodati tudi k različici izdelka, ne pa "
"predlogi izdelka. Obrazec dokumenta za različico izdelka je enak obrazcu "
"dokumenta predloge izdelka, **razen** da ne vključuje razdelka *E-trgovina* "
"in zato ga ni mogoče objaviti na spletni strani."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:41
msgid ""
"To add a PDF to a product variant, navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales app "
"--> Products --> Product Variants`, select the product variant, click "
"the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button, and :ref:`upload the PDF <sales/"
"pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products/add-pdf-to-product>`."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati PDF k različici izdelka, pojdite v "
":menuselection:`Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Različice izdelkov`, izberite "
"različico izdelka, kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Dokumenti` in "
":ref:`naložite PDF <sales/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products/add-pdf-to-"
"product>`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:46
msgid ""
"If the variant is added to a quotation, and there are documents on a product "
"*and* on its variant, **only** the documents in the variant are shown in the "
"*Quote Builder* tab of the quotation."
msgstr ""
"Če je različica dodana k ponudbi in obstajajo dokumenti na izdelku *in* na "
"njegovi različici, so v zavihku *Izdelovalec ponudb* ponudbe prikazani "
"**samo** dokumenti v različici."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:53
msgid "Document form configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija obrazca dokumenta"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:56
msgid ""
"To save a document form entry, the user **must** add a URL or PDF to the "
"document form. Odoo won't save the entry without one, even if the rest of "
"the form is configured."
msgstr ""
"Če želite shraniti vnos obrazca dokumenta, **mora** uporabnik dodati URL ali "
"PDF v obrazec dokumenta. Odoo ne bo shranil vnosa brez njega, tudi če je "
"preostanek obrazca konfiguriran."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:60
msgid "General Information"
msgstr "Splošne informacije"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:62
msgid ""
"Fill out the following information in the top section of the document form:"
msgstr "Izpolnite naslednje informacije v zgornjem delu obrazca dokumenta:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:64
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Type`: Select either :guilabel:`File` or a :guilabel:`URL` from "
"the drop-down menu. If a PDF is uploaded, the :guilabel:`Type` field is "
"automatically set to :guilabel:`File` and cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vrsta`: V spustnem meniju izberite :guilabel:`Datoteka` ali "
":guilabel:`URL`. Če je PDF naložen, se polje :guilabel:`Vrsta` samodejno "
"nastavi na :guilabel:`Datoteka` in ga ni mogoče spremeniti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:67
msgid ""
":guilabel:`URL`: This field is only clickable if the :guilabel:`Type` field "
"is set to :guilabel:`URL`. Enter a URL link to an online PDF document."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`URL`: To polje je mogoče klikniti samo, če je polje "
":guilabel:`Vrsta` nastavljeno na :guilabel:`URL`. Vnesite povezavo URL do "
"spletnega dokumenta PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:69
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Name`: This field is grayed out (not clickable) until a URL is "
"entered or a PDF is uploaded. If the URL is entered, the :guilabel:`Name` "
"field is left blank, and it can then be edited. If a PDF document has been "
"uploaded, the :guilabel:`Name` field is auto-populated with the file name, "
"and it can then be edited."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ime`: To polje je sivo (ni mogoče klikniti), dokler ni vnesen URL "
"ali naložen PDF. Če je vnesen URL, je polje :guilabel:`Ime` prazno in ga je "
"nato mogoče urediti. Če je bil naložen dokument PDF, se polje "
":guilabel:`Ime` samodejno izpolni z imenom datoteke in ga je nato mogoče "
"urediti."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:73
msgid ""
":guilabel:`File Content (base64)`: This field displays the uploaded file. "
"Click it to open the file directory and select a different PDF."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Vsebina datoteke (base64)`: To polje prikazuje naloženo datoteko. "
"Kliknite ga, da odprete imenik datotek in izberete drug PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:75
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Edit)` icon: Click to open the file directory "
"and select a different PDF."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-pencil` :guilabel:`(Uredi)` ikona: Kliknite, da odprete imenik "
"datotek in izberete drug PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:77
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`(Download)` icon: Click to download the PDF "
"document. This icon only appears after a PDF is uploaded and the document "
"form is saved."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-download` :guilabel:`(Prenesi)` ikona: Kliknite, da prenesete "
"dokument PDF. Ta ikona se pojavi šele po naložitvi PDF in shranitvi obrazca "
"dokumenta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:79
msgid ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Delete)` icon: Click to remove the uploaded "
"PDF. This action allows the user to change the :guilabel:`Type` field "
"from :guilabel:`File` to :guilabel:`URL` and enter a URL link instead."
msgstr ""
":icon:`fa-trash` :guilabel:`(Izbriši)` ikona: Kliknite, da odstranite "
"naloženi PDF. To dejanje uporabniku omogoča, da spremeni polje "
":guilabel:`Vrsta` iz :guilabel:`Datoteka` v :guilabel:`URL` in namesto tega "
"vnese povezavo URL."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:82
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Configure dynamic fields`: Click the link if the PDF document or "
"URL has dynamic form fields that need to be :ref:`configured to Odoo fields "
"<sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/map-PDF-to-Odoo>`. If the PDF document "
"or URL has custom dynamic form fields, refer to the :ref:`sales/"
"pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/custom-dynamic-form-fields` for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Konfiguriraj dinamična polja`: Kliknite povezavo, če ima dokument "
"PDF ali URL dinamična polja obrazca, ki jih je treba :ref:`konfigurirati na "
"polja Odoo <sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/map-PDF-to-Odoo>`. Če ima "
"dokument PDF ali URL polja obrazca po meri dinamičnih polj, glejte "
":ref:`sales/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/custom-dynamic-form-fields` za "
"več informacij."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:None
msgid "A standard document form with an uploaded pdf in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Standardni obrazec dokumenta z naloženim pdf-jem v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:94
#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:130
msgid ""
"Click the :guilabel:`Sale: Visible at` field and select one of the following "
"options:"
msgstr ""
"Kliknite polje :guilabel:`Prodaja: Vidno pri` in izberite eno od naslednjih "
"možnosti:"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:96
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hidden`: The PDF or URL isn't visible in the **Sales** app. This "
"option is best for digital product documents intended for publication on the "
"website, but not shown in the quotation or customer portal."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Skrito`: PDF ali URL ni viden v aplikaciji **Prodaja**. Ta "
"možnost je najboljša za digitalne dokumente izdelkov, namenjene objavi na "
"spletni strani, vendar niso prikazani v ponudbi ali portalu za stranke."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:99
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On quote`: The PDF document or URL can be sent to customers at "
"any time. It is also available for download on the customer portal. This "
"options is best for product description files."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`V ponudbi`: Dokument PDF ali URL je mogoče kadarkoli poslati "
"strankam. Na voljo je tudi za prenos na portalu za stranke. Ta možnost je "
"najboljša za datoteke z opisi izdelkov."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:101
msgid ""
":guilabel:`On confirmed order`: The PDF document or URL is sent to customers "
"upon order confirmation. It is available on the customer port after a "
"quotation is confirmed. This is best for user manuals and digital content "
"sold on eCommerce websites."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ob potrjenem naročilu`: Dokument PDF ali URL je poslan strankam "
"ob potrditvi naročila. Na voljo je na portalu za stranke po potrditvi "
"ponudbe. To je najboljše za uporabniška navodila in digitalno vsebino, "
"prodano na spletnih straneh e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:104
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Inside quote`: The PDF document or URL is included in the PDF "
"quotation, between the header pages and the :guilabel:`Pricing` section."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Znotraj ponudbe`: Dokument PDF ali URL je vključen v ponudbo PDF, "
"med stranmi glave in razdelkom :guilabel:`Oblikovanje cen`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:108
msgid ""
"When the :guilabel:`On quote` option for the :guilabel:`Visible at` field is "
"selected and the custom PDF document, `AC product info and warranty.pdf`, is "
"uploaded, the PDF appears in the *customer portal* quotation in "
"the :guilabel:`Documents` section."
msgstr ""
"Ko je izbrana možnost :guilabel:`Ob ponudbi` za polje :guilabel:`Vidno pri` "
"in je naložen dokument PDF po meri, `AC product info and warranty.pdf`, se "
"PDF prikaže v ponudbi *portala za stranke* v razdelku :guilabel:`Dokumenti`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:0
msgid ""
"Sample of an uploaded pdf with the on quote option chosen in Odoo Sales."
msgstr "Vzorec naloženega PDF-ja z izbrano možnostjo pri ponudbi v Odoo Sales."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:116
msgid "E-Commerce section"
msgstr "Razdelek E-trgovina"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:118
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Publish on Website`: A checkbox that, if enabled, displays a link "
"to download the PDF document on the product page in the online store."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Objavi na spletni strani`: Potrditveno polje, ki, če je "
"omogočeno, prikaže povezavo za prenos dokumenta PDF na strani izdelka v "
"spletni trgovini."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:0
msgid "An uploaded document on an e-commerce product page."
msgstr "Naložen dokument na strani izdelka e-trgovine."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:125
msgid "Manufacturing section"
msgstr "Razdelek Proizvodnja"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:128
msgid "This section only appears if the **Manufacturing** app is installed."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek se prikaže samo, če je nameščena aplikacija **Proizvodnja**."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Hidden`: The PDF or URL is accessible only on the product form."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Skrito`: PDF ali URL je dostopen samo na obrazcu izdelka."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:133
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Bill of Materials`: The PDF or URL is attached to the bill of "
"materials when the product is manufactured. This option is best for assembly "
"instructions and manufacturing specifications."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Kosovnica`: PDF ali URL je priložen kosovnici, ko je izdelek "
"proizveden. Ta možnost je najboljša za navodila za sestavljanje in "
"proizvodne specifikacije."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:140
msgid "View all configured PDFs or links for a product"
msgstr "Ogled vseh konfiguriranih datotek PDF ali povezav za izdelek"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:142
msgid ""
"Navigate to the :menuselection:`Sales app --> Products --> Products` and "
"select a product. Click the :guilabel:`Documents` smart button to open "
"the :guilabel:`Documents` page and display all the documents for the product "
"template and its variants. File and URL cards can be visually distinguished "
"by the images in the left corner. A PDF thumbnail is for PDF documents, and "
"a :icon:`fa-link` :guilabel:`link` icon is for URL links. For product "
"variants documents, a *Variant* badge is to be displayed in the corner as "
"well."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Izdelki --> Izdelki` in "
"izberite izdelek. Kliknite pametni gumb :guilabel:`Dokumenti`, da odprete "
"stran :guilabel:`Dokumenti` in prikažete vse dokumente za predlogo izdelka "
"in njene različice. Kartice datotek in URL-jev je mogoče vizualno "
"razlikovati po slikah v levem kotu. Sličica PDF je za dokumente PDF, ikona "
":icon:`fa-link` :guilabel:`povezava` pa je za povezave URL. Za dokumente "
"različic izdelka se v kotu prikaže tudi značka *Različica*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:None
msgid ""
"PDFs form cards of a product in the Sales app and one has a variant badge."
msgstr ""
"Kartice obrazcev PDF izdelka v aplikaciji Prodaja in ena ima značko "
"različice."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_products.rst:153
msgid ":doc:`dynamic_text`"
msgstr ":doc:`dynamic_text`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:3
msgid "Add PDFs to a quote"
msgstr "Dodajanje datotek PDF ponudbi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:5
msgid ""
"PDFs can be manually added to a quote as a header or footer, or as an "
"additional PDF to be merged with the quote details. They can be accessed "
"from the *Quote Builder* tab on a quotation. A quote can have multiple "
"headers or footers selected. If a quote has multiple headers or footers, "
"they are merged together in the order they were selected, with the quote "
"details in between."
msgstr ""
"Datoteke PDF je mogoče ročno dodati ponudbi kot glavo ali nogo ali kot "
"dodatno datoteko PDF, ki se združi s podrobnostmi ponudbe. Dostopne so na "
"zavihku *Graditelj ponudbe* na ponudbi. Ponudba ima lahko več izbranih glav "
"ali nog. Če ima ponudba več glav ali nog, se združijo skupaj v vrstnem redu, "
"v katerem so bile izbrane, s podrobnostmi ponudbe vmes."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:11
msgid "Add headers and footers to a quote"
msgstr "Dodajanje glav in nog ponudbi"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:13
msgid ""
"Navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> Quotations` and select the desired "
"quotation. Click the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab, and all available "
"headers and footers are displayed in their own self-titled sections. If any "
"products have PDFs attached on their form, then a :guilabel:`Product` "
"section displays."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na :menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Ponudbe` in izberite "
"želeno ponudbo. Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudbe` in vse "
"razpoložljive glave in noge so prikazane v svojih razdelkih z lastnim "
"naslovom. Če ima kateri koli izdelek priložene datoteke PDF na svojem "
"obrazcu, se prikaže razdelek :guilabel:`Izdelek`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:18
msgid ""
"Select the additional PDFs to be merged into the final PDF. If a selected "
"PDF contains :ref:`custom note form fields <sales/pdf_quote_builder/"
"dynamic_text/custom-note>`, they appear as editable text boxes to be filled "
"in."
msgstr ""
"Izberite dodatne datoteke PDF, ki bodo združene v končno datoteko PDF. Če "
"izbrana datoteka PDF vsebuje :ref:`polja obrazca za opombe po meri <sales/"
"pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text/custom-note>`, se prikažejo kot urejevalna "
"besedilna polja za izpolnjevanje."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Quote Builder tab with selected headers and footers. Custom note form "
"fields are\n"
"displayed."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Graditelj ponudbe z izbranimi glavami in nogami. Prikazana so polja "
"obrazca za\n"
"opombe po meri."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:26
msgid ""
"Odoo provides the option to print a PDF of the quote for record keeping. To "
"print the PDF quote, navigate to the confirmed quote, and click "
"the :icon:`fa-cog` :menuselection:`Actions --> Print --> PDF Quote`."
msgstr ""
"Odoo omogoča možnost tiskanja datoteke PDF ponudbe za arhiviranje. Za "
"tiskanje ponudbe PDF pojdite na potrjeno ponudbo in kliknite :icon:`fa-cog` "
":menuselection:`Dejanja --> Tiskanje --> PDF ponudba`."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:None
msgid "A sales order drop-down menu with the option to Print PDF Quote."
msgstr "Spustni meni prodajnega naloga z možnostjo Tiskanje ponudbe PDF."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:33
msgid ""
"Open the PDF quote file to confirm the configured header, footer, and "
"additional PDFs before printing."
msgstr ""
"Odprite datoteko PDF ponudbe, da potrdite konfigurirane glave, noge in "
"dodatne PDF-je pred tiskanjem."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:37
msgid ""
"Download these :download:`PDF quote builder examples <add_pdf_quotes/"
"pdfquotebuilderexamples.zip>` or this :download:`sample quotation "
"<add_pdf_quotes/sample_quotation.pdf>` for additional reference."
msgstr ""
"Prenesite te :download:`primere graditelja PDF ponudb <add_pdf_quotes/"
"pdfquotebuilderexamples.zip>` ali to :download:`vzorčno ponudbo "
"<add_pdf_quotes/sample_quotation.pdf>` za dodatno referenco."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:42
msgid ""
"A car dealership wants to include its vehicle purchase order form with each "
"quotation. They create a PDF template of the form and upload it to the "
"**Sales** app as a header."
msgstr ""
"Prodajalec avtomobilov želi vključiti obrazec za naročilo vozila v vsako "
"ponudbo. Ustvari predlogo PDF obrazca in jo naloži v aplikacijo **Prodaja** "
"kot glavo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:45
msgid ""
"When they create a quote for a customer, they select the header in the "
"*Quote Builder* tab and manually fill in the customized note form fields."
msgstr ""
"Ko ustvarijo ponudbo za stranko, v zavihku *Graditelj ponudbe* izberejo "
"glavo in ročno izpolnijo polja obrazca s prilagojenim opombom."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Quote Builder tab with a vehicle purchase order form selected as the "
"header."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek Graditelj ponudbe z obrazcem za naročilo vozila, izbranim kot glava."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:51
msgid ""
"After the quote has been signed and confirmed, the car seller downloads and "
"prints a copy of the PDF quote for the customer. The PDF quote contains the "
"vehicle purchase order form as the header, the quote details in the body, "
"and the dealership's standard footer."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ponudba podpisana in potrjena, prodajalec avtomobilov prenese in "
"natisne kopijo PDF ponudbe za stranko. PDF ponudba vsebuje obrazec za "
"naročilo vozila kot glavo, podrobnosti ponudbe v telesu in standardno nogo "
"prodajnega mesta."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:56
msgid "Add headers and footers to a quote template"
msgstr "Dodajanje glav in nog v predlogo ponudbe"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:59
msgid ""
"Headers and footers added to a quote template are **only** available when "
"that template is applied — they won't appear as standalone header/footer "
"options for quotes."
msgstr ""
"Glave in noge, dodane v predlogo ponudbe, so na voljo **samo**, ko je ta "
"predloga uporabljena — ne bodo se prikazale kot samostojne možnosti za glave/"
"noge pri ponudbah."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:62
msgid ""
"To add PDFs to a quote template, navigate to :menuselection:`Sales app --> "
"Configuration --> Quote Templates`, and select the desired template. Click "
"the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab and click :guilabel:`Add Headers and "
"footers`. In the *Add: Headers and footers* pop-up, select the PDF to be "
"added to the quote template. Selected PDFs are displayed in "
"the :guilabel:`Quote Builder` tab as cards."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati PDF-je v predlogo ponudbe, pojdite na "
":menuselection:`Aplikacija Prodaja --> Konfiguracija --> Predloge ponudb` in "
"izberite želeno predlogo. Kliknite zavihek :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudbe` in "
"kliknite :guilabel:`Dodaj glave in noge`. V pojavnem oknu *Dodaj: Glave in "
"noge* izberite PDF, ki ga želite dodati v predlogo ponudbe. Izbrani PDF-ji "
"so prikazani v zavihku :guilabel:`Graditelj ponudbe` kot kartice."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:68
msgid ""
"To remove a header or footer, click the :icon:`fa-ellipsis-"
"v` :guilabel:`vertical ellipsis` icon on the card and "
"select :guilabel:`Delete`. Deleting a header or footer from a quote template "
"only removes it from the template. It remains available in the *Quote "
"Builder* tab and the *Headers/Footers* page."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odstraniti glavo ali nogo, kliknite ikono :icon:`fa-ellipsis-v` "
":guilabel:`navpične tri pike` na kartici in izberite :guilabel:`Izbriši`. "
"Brisanje glave ali noge iz predloge ponudbe jo odstrani samo iz predloge. "
"Ostane na voljo v zavihku *Graditelj ponudbe* in na strani *Glave/noge*."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/add_pdf_quotes.rst:74
msgid ":doc:`../quote_template`"
msgstr ":doc:`../quote_template`"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:8
msgid "Configure dynamic form fields in PDFs"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje dinamičnih polj obrazca v PDF-jih"

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:10
msgid ""
"When creating custom PDFs to import into the **Sales** app, use *dynamic "
"form fields* to auto-fill the PDF content with relevant information from the "
"Odoo database, including names and prices."
msgstr ""
"Pri ustvarjanju prilagojenih PDF-jev za uvoz v aplikacijo **Prodaja** "
"uporabite *dinamična polja obrazca*, da samodejno izpolnite vsebino PDF z "
"ustreznimi informacijami iz baze podatkov Odoo, vključno z imeni in cenami."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:13
msgid ""
"*Dynamic form fields* are configurable text fields that can be added to a "
"PDF form, and Odoo automatically fills them with values from the sales order/"
"product associated with the quote."
msgstr ""
"*Dinamična polja obrazca* so konfigurabilna besedilna polja, ki jih lahko "
"dodate v obrazec PDF, Odoo pa jih samodejno izpolni z vrednostmi iz "
"prodajnega naloga/izdelka, povezanega s ponudbo."

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/sales_quotations/pdf_quote_builder/dynamic_text.rst:17
